[{"Name":"Disha Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9RvTMXeP3KqSHfnATMTo2ic7srx022rxbo_TaCIeCacEG1IXQ0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband Loved their lamb - it was cooked to perfection, the flavour was incredible! Will definitely be there whenever I crave home food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdKRU0TtCufucesFLWgvgnCVrqub2aU6UcucQy&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"N√¥MƒÅR √Ölt√Ø√ß≈Ç√∂≈õ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKVyqW_kOlfqb-yGJ_Ks--LFkl55GXHpZ6S3YNX2dqaycCck_x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely a great place to go at New Westminster. A+++","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0yG2ePykRZVqVp9bv_zhmiISD5RKuQVMvIvZq&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Andrea Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM4pS0EMj65wD2yAVVGQIpVP4NowO8zIGvLgz5WtH9vuZgfj2lUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For 4 people, we ordered the 1/2 Sujuk & Kashkaval cheese and 1/2 Chicken Taouk flatbread, as well as the Lamb shank. The combos also came with a huge pita with 4 different dips, which were all very flavourful and delicious. The Negroni cocktail was also great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOF6iC59vZ0zj9uGemUc8zokRwEwedaee3CunWa&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Sally Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYImJyCsPZ1U003tXN4fpaHQosVQMfmFbKD19gt9ySf-YRWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The flavor of the Manoushe was delicious! We ordered the spicy cheese one and the kofta one, and both were excellent. On the other hand, some Lebanese food staples like the hummus and Fattoush salad were disappointing, tasteless  and far from authentic Lebanese flavor.

The place is very nice and comfortable; however, the service is another weak point. We had a waiter at first who never took our order, we called him but he ignored us. So we asked assistance from another waiter, and he made a huge difference. A very friendly and efficient Chilean young man. He was the only staff member who properly attended to the customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlI-C8Higuhtg40r0D-YindgoaxLDDzvvUP2JC&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Denis Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF32K7mKkPkKCpGUSEjmRXhqYloH84bwlSW6sQJ_X-vjOnAtXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At Wild Thyme, the prices may be a bit higher than average for the area, but the food is undeniably authentic and bursting with flavor. While the service can be slow on occasion, the delicious dishes make it worth the wait. The ambience is very simple. The restaurant's commitment to authentic cuisine shines through in every bite. Overall, Wild Thyme is a great choice for those looking for a flavorful dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNf9EFK7vQvqMKcPi8FRHFxojJHnWj_k2llGZbf&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Kyna Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeAn18U7f9LuHN2nbEK91_Xr_RYuaJ54cNr9CH_ah-OcrfCgjwPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious manuoush‚Äôeh flatbread. Had the kafta and kashkaval.was delicious and huge, albeit quite costly.
My friend enjoyed her chicken wrap too.
Great service and ambience! Thanks for a delicious meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-76jk_dfL28BUN8qBoGy4iwWjmQHikLGgrHma&fid=0x0:0x6be6b5b1e7999279"],"When":"2024-10-19"}]

[{"Name":"Harry Beik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsr6XlTHZrjz94XPyuJ8B3E7luW3WvAYpMmlcf8C0ZluUHmNwP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I've ordered from this Pizza Hut location several times and have generally been satisfied. However, tonight, for the first time, I ordered the XL size and was very disappointed with the quality. The pizza not only lacked a good flavor but also didn‚Äôt look appealing, as you can see in the photo, and it was excessively greasy. I really don't understand why the pizza's quality should drop just because I ordered a larger size!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHA3e-IMzg2r0e3z81L3DdjtRk-CTB1nuPTh-I&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their $10.00 Margherita pizza was bomb and the tomatoes on them were real tomatoes that were flavourful and juicy too. It's pizza!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4fTHOjmL6J-bfOqkqK2ELYO51IwB-jVRKdXyO&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2022-4-12"},{"Name":"Coey H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL16t349ITgAYmpkMsHuSPnQjVUtk354A6hoMbEbk8JeYOtPA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not recommend. Attention! They have such a low rates can really tell something. See how greasy their crust is. Unlike other pizzas I had before, the crust tastes like deep fired food! If the baking thing takes a short cut to deep fry, it‚Äôs really like a cheat. Besides,there isn‚Äôt the good special smell of baking food in the crust, but a smell of greasy oil. And I hope they DON‚ÄôT use the Hydrogenated vegetable oil which is well used in the fries or some junk food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPp4bkzfMKChrwaE-BsPyPpD72Xdu2pwOPbiA6K&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2022-1-12"},{"Name":"Andrew K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1G4i0IJLWg2b692jv6KSAow9P8XKkjr-ijI5pF7_pK5fHYEJJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pizza was very hot and fresh. Ordered stuffed crust vegetarian lover + added hot peppers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlW8a6Vi0niAZrHoTLWNw2IqyFPkA3I2Jxl7-B&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Johnny G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBbi4rvv-nHDl7H6RXbToA_kk3n9Hj_ierIgyWzQHyZr_63w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice friendly service, perfect pizza for after my gambling sessions to soak up all the booze I drink. This pizza really opens my mind up to what plans I should be building in the casino. I will be better and win every day. I know I can do it. You'll see. I'll win with a slice in hand, thank you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQI92qzIvxYHVG2Wv6_ByEIInKHnOqp62u67Ka&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2023-6-24"},{"Name":"Jennifer Chien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-uYhM0OXW4Bap9syuvpsHqoSYb15hZFK9fcmHJjm-ueRjbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered the wings and pizzas for delivery from Uber Eats.

The Hawaiian and flatbread pizzas were passable. All of the pizzas I received were a bit too brown so the crust got very hard. The honey garlic wings were good, but a bit too salty. The worst part of my order was the popcorn chicken pizza. Incredibly dry and no sign of any gravy. I would not recommend ordering the popcorn chicken pizza from this location.

Overall, it's a decent place to get some pizza, but there are better places out there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxPF2wnT2laaKK-V25Z-N-cZ3leS5GbbrfF8jw&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2021-6-26"},{"Name":"janela domingo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb9gq_OtC41ARc6PivdAMQI30aUYScFIv1sytwPoC71W3Ofzoe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible experience as you can obviously see that there's a hair on the pizza.. and we ordered the sauce but didn't see it when we got home. Its our first time buying in here and we are just really disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgSqN48U9HvdoNhl3J7MBO_OIL_1yl5INi7wpf&fid=0x0:0xf6337137bed5855a"],"When":"2021-11-14"},{"Name":"Dante BroadFord","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiMKbRTICB9Qu3PkOmn8GBxNCQ80zY66ZflcRWat9fXnQPvUU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic experience at Pizza Hut! [{"Name":"Samrat Roy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-bYH4-yBOtNeXL4jqm3AOzFqHmewwl6Z80LgPdRXMd2gACbHH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"When we visited Jokim Kitchen in the evening, it wasn‚Äôt busy at all, which made for a relaxed dining experience. The M·∫πt B√∫n Th·∫≠p C·∫©m Platter as well as lemongrass chicken rice was delicious, and the service was okay. It‚Äôs a cozy spot in New Westminster with great food and a calm atmosphere, perfect for an unhurried meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2SLK9mmOma9z99QERtaJdcVsQjBBai6Noa34M&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There was plenty of seating when we arrived. We got lemongrass chicken and it was juicy and flavourful. The bbq platter was underwhelming as it came with Chinese chicken wings which I didn‚Äôt realize was extremely spicy. I never had Chinese chicken wings like this. The skewered prawns was also spicy but not as bad as the wings. Homemade sausage was delicious and I loved the large chunks of garlic in it. The beef ribs were a lower quality you will need teeth to eat it or scissors but flavour was delicious. We also for a papaya salad with beef jerky as I wasn‚Äôt full from the bbq platter. It paired well together with the beef jerky.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwaJwKBt_KnpAz94sWSekevdiDrGOBZD2qsfNf&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Gina Grape","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjfpAS0e1J9DlXOCRvxRrfnAvo44TyYUw59aPp0ohD7GacQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good ambience inside.  A hole on the wall kinda of gem in Uptown New West. Great food and portion for your buck.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbKfhWZgiqe-B3nUCu02TypZb3vv8O3BZfBjFq&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Shulamie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtB81aCg4AAdMLOwFvnHlpdLkbB43qZuPbkeepGzXQ192dANwppA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Our experience at Jokim was okay overall. About 3/4 of the tables were full during our visit on a Friday evening, but only one waitress working. The bun bo hue was good, the pho dac biet was okay, spring rolls were good but very thin, and the mango prawn salad was too sour (used too much filler marinated radish). Unfortunately won't be back as our experience, though not bad, wasn't great either.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOln2uOL1viXYxF1GvAAtqOPPL2BD02Plu5z5a2&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Alexander Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQHN0Aa0rJYdoqcfcagGbfOH-0cvC7psAXsBkP3P2cBz16RQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I went to Jokim for the first time and it was fantastic. The whole place was beautiful, clean, and had both a modern and relaxed vibe with low-fi music. We were greeted openly with a smile and sat down to see the menu. Our food came quickly, beautifully plated, and everything tasted amazing. The whole experience from start to finish was a delight. The portions were perfect, prices were more than reasonable. I really can't wait to go again and try something else on the menu.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcus C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHlnwaovl3zd5Wc5SMTrMR58MAbhW47-67QJsaGLwyfRDvio4XoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time checking this place out and I was pleasantly surprised! Went here for a quick lunch and got the steak and the lady got vermicelli and both were so tasty! The sauce on the steak was next level and with an egg it made it that much better. The vermicelli was a perfect and filling dish for the lady as well. I'm looking forward to trying out the platter next time we come! Thanks for the great service, food and atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8_84XbjO5zxBoVrtaH5zOl2FqXLf8mBEVa010&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2023-2-12"},{"Name":"Lee Jay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzDtMsWCn-NlUmLWHN1-Vcx1s1iKHSJVkIwJ44E45omza3tzcN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ate in many Vietnamese restaurants before, if you are looking for delicious Vietnamese food with affordable price, good customer service and generous food portion then this is the right place!

I ordered spicy noodle soup, they putted in real broth which they already cooked for 16 hours (not just water).

Jokim is the best and I will recommended to everyone!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHW2ImNbd78zO2Jt9fQ7IKVxFFs5L3dd3IlVqn&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2023-4-16"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow, just wow! The Saigon platter was excellent! I didn't know grilled galangal pork can taste this good. The grilled beef in petel leaves was so juicy. I also love their mini pancakes, crispy bottom and rich coconut flavor inside. Fruit smoothies (avocado & mango) were okay, the flavor was not strong but the texture was creamy. Nice & attentive waitress.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv2IksPCj6nJorm8StjZX4ISFAuOiHu4klHrrR&fid=0x0:0x6631c1699c6230ad"],"When":"2023-7-8"}]

[{"Name":"Hiep Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMRHHZ7t798igHqhwEObqqiXXBYRe7_vTRRS3-gXG7fOgZlXSH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time at Big Way Hot Pot and so I had high expectations since they have many locations and many ppl talk about it. I've also had hot pot at many different hot pot places so will be comparing based on those experiences.

1. Great selection, however it ended up tasting the same like any other place once everything is in the pot.
2. Lining up to get your own food was long, felt like I'm at a food court.
3. We paid by weighing everything in the pot. Mine was $36 üòÆ.  But we got free tea and ice cream at the end.
4. Many servers always asking how things are, but my friends food came 15 min after mine. I didn't eat til his came. My food wasn't as hot anymore.
5. Great view out their window. This place used to be a pub. Interior decor was nice and spacious, good energy.

Yes, I would come back here again if I was in New West. I know what to do next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3at6-mEjYzjDhA-wX3gN7WPffYL1J2thcIBHG&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"AIZY A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW63HuUeCCv9sgK_rgm18cZfVwLP0r1WfmUCdIu1jqRWz_XpAFKzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It started getting busy right after we were seated. The service was excellent, and we loved being able to choose exactly what we wanted in our soup and create our own dipping sauce. Plus, the view from our window seat was beautiful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfL8SuU1pDh6NdSe2QjKIDXLAdD0uytmivGTr6&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Soung Son","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHkihcNrKz3Cs19caeCuVOR-Yk29MFxtD_S6stmS9PXtHqts7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time here and first time ever at Big Way. Food was good, the broth surprised us. We got the mushroom broth and the savory broth. The mushroom is the way to go.

If it‚Äôs your first time. Get here when it‚Äôs not rush hour and you gotta get in the waitlist then once ready. They give you a pot and you go ahead and place all the ingredients you want inside your pot and then it gets weighed and you pay.

Then take your table flag and sit anywhere you like. I wish the instruction was explained as nobody really explained it but it wasn‚Äôt too hard to figure out

Interior is nice still looks similar to the previous business (bar). Overall a solid 3.5 experience and we would come back for sure","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM40cD640NJi-hC3SeWxNPzxj0nFezbsxu43zcN&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Sherry Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJj8Y2C9f-lxQ3f0Wg6KMNVI7g0Vcpm8w53WH722rbEZ4-8Jnf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my friend visited on one of the busiest night of the week. The staffs are very accommodating and friendly even though we were late to the reservation. Food and drinks are so delicious! For broth, I highly recommend the tomato dry mix and szechuan green pepper. For drink I love the tea, super affordable and yummy. Service is excellent as well!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOK3iO6y6hwNnJSaGSj3v3N5uRaHG6JSPovWQy&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Seinn Moh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3eoiEdZ-Q1IRrKZzncaIBXgDNXSSmr15bmZ4YTKV-pRLAoDZR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing dining experience at Big Way Hot Pot! A special thanks to Kay Z for her outstanding service! She was incredibly friendly, attentive, and made sure we had everything we needed throughout our meal. Her warm personality truly added to the overall experience. Thank you, Kay Z, for making our visit so enjoyable!
I highly recommend Big Way Hot Pot and will definitely be back soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFKdLtbT0-fgYlzlwJ00-X4G6uP9ALb_a247Pt&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Paul Rondeau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWud2O79gqkHkgkw8XLlTly4855w4zQuECqNb6Iq_cxHMS3y4p-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great hot pot spot! Worth the wait. As soon as you enter, you‚Äôre provided with a huge bowl to fill up with all the ingredients of your choice before it‚Äôs weighed and then you pick your broth/soup flavour. Everything was great! Load up on seafood, meat and veggies. Try the collagen bone broth flavour - it was tasty. You will also have a full sauce bar to add spice or other flavours. There are SO many staff/servers which was great. My only complaint is that everyone‚Äôs bowl arrived at a very different time. I hope this place can sort this out since it‚Äôs a little annoying to wait to eat for others when your soup cools. Can‚Äôt wait to return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_OQ5ybaDnNazODPRS2eKoA2RM46smKGwUCQPw&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Hannah Nguon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMhvv9ggaZa8CF9qSvuYmrA6EwdW6vVOlwPPtoTJ-P8n_jyMI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Similar to other Big Way locations. I felt like the food here is saltier? The pots were dented and only the pork shoulder rolls (?) were actually in rolls, everything else was just in shredded pieces and sort of frozen still. The servers were nice but the cashier was mumbling a bit and I felt like I was annoying him by asking him to repeat himself. My food came in approx. 10 minutes but my friend‚Äôs took 20. I began eating immediately and noticed everything was overcooked. Also, the customers sitting next to us were speaking to a server who misplaced their orders, when they got new orders, it was still the wrong one. The ice cream here is way smaller than the other locations. Most of the other reviews are also saying these things. It‚Äôs closer to Surrey which I appreciate, but I would rather just go to the Metrotown locations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOM4xn-wJE8ksE7URnvVlX2kVgZs2bs79jpq1-a&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Carmen Aboytes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCCLFKJlS62-34BUpujZzDsaZV9yysTxPBmk8fhCY7OoETeMyS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time here and first time ever at Big Way!

If it‚Äôs your first time, here‚Äôs how it works: try to come during non-peak hours to avoid the rush. You‚Äôll need to join the waitlist, and once it‚Äôs your turn, you‚Äôll get a pot. Then, you can pick and add all the ingredients you want into your pot. It‚Äôs weighed at the end, and you pay based on the weight. We gor to excited, and we paid $119 with a tip (2 ppl)

Afterward, grab your table flag and sit wherever you like. The process is straightforward, but a tip: the broth can get *really* hot, so be cautious‚Äîit can make it hard to fully enjoy your meal for a while.

Also, if you don‚Äôt want to wait too long, I highly recommend joining the waitlist online before you arrive. You‚Äôll be able to see how many parties are ahead of you and plan your arrival better. Sometimes there can be over 100 parties ahead, which can mean a wait time of 1-2 hours. Planning ahead is key for a smoother experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPk6l5mUSjGHG0iP8rgD-Ka-XEsFHwUD-kBnZb&fid=0x0:0x234a3872f78b5ebc"],"When":"2024-12-21"}]

The restaurant itself was clean and had a comfortable atmosphere, perfect for a casual meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rhaymart Martirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoew8w-vlKn93HWxCSOgqLBUzhkhLkBx5zN4-lHNfYiHoFKgk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"‚ÄúA Hidden Gem for Donair Lovers!‚Äù

My wife and I truly enjoyed this dish. Made to perfection with a plethora of taste in one dish. Definitely will be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy95ROxUfleXIDFEGfkChj6hLFPOzb0gPMknf7&fid=0x0:0x68ebc9aff9d9b505"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Gee Ewing","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeZ4OP5M7fsWVAitA-fGvuWB8KuZtq-Dd9VVZ3Ee5TqmP50g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My coworker and I picked the restaurant simply because we had never had East African food before!
I have no experience with this cuisine, so I can't speak to the authenticity of it, but it was FANTASTIC.
I had the veggie combo, and as a big eater, I couldn't eat all of it, so A+ on the portion size.
My coworker had lamb of sorts, and it was quite tasty as well.
The person working, was very friendly, and the food came out quite quickly as well. In and out in 35 minutes made this a great lunch time meal for us.
I'd eat here again!
The only thing I was surprised about though, thought there would be some chicken options. Not a complaint, just an observation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYhWpoIPDY9xkr2aET2Ctau9A23n_8wPyJnME-&fid=0x0:0x68ebc9aff9d9b505"],"When":"2022-10-8"},{"Name":"James Kan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVk_o12iCtyO0gE_QoPCj5qJ7UUQkuic2cEzUnsQvn8LpSf4EV-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have tried African injera 11 years ago in Saskatoon, however, the restaurant closed.
I am great my best friend brought me here, to have delicious African food again.
Very good price for each order you want to pick, and they serve pretty much twice as you need food.
Injera is well known a sour flavour pancake, which looks many holes on the top of the flat bread. Soft pancake with hundreds of hole, put those meat or sauces on, that is maximum those food tasted in mouth.
I would love to come again and again for the injera meals.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9fhz1B0r-K7SpK5Mxvg4O0S-QCTiWI0CnnykC&fid=0x0:0x68ebc9aff9d9b505"],"When":"2023-8-7"},{"Name":"silveryfeather208","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIV1DAc6oAZcKGUjDYKQfX3Js6BWSD-KkYIFsB6AYpaKFALg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have no other ethiopian restaurant to compare this too, but portion for price is so wonderful. Although the food wasn't extra special, it tasted fresh and hearty, and price is great, so I give it 5 stars. Service is good! Cute little atmosphere there too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Azeb A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfQ9puc9EZxXlJr3oAzuQuWGM9s2aTgc1mtth6hNFiaTTX7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Massawa restaurant has accommodated  our big family with children for a dinner. The food was really good especially the Tibs. The waitress was amazing, welcoming, and very proportional. According to our group of coffee lovers, the coffee they had had the best taste with a hint of ginger. Our gratitude goes out to the waitress for the amazing service she provided us and for taking care of the other customers in the restaurant even though she was the only one there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Ferguson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVClrrX_-Wt5j3aCHo-S6JYfETzTRqLkHzGlV5LFh0G3R32gm8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent food, very tasty and reasonably priced. Noisy (popular!) which made it a bit hard to hear our server, who missed our son's order. She was very apologetic and they whipped up his order immediately after being informed. Highly tasty and looking forward to going again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIK-DCBsPJNLqz9uCGurtNTgtdmj-8vS4HxnlC&fid=0x0:0x68ebc9aff9d9b505"],"When":"2021-8-10"},{"Name":"Selam Herba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgr-rflxntENOwMfWKRJI_DoSn1gfsxzwe9vZkiBk6IrjoNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delighted with their new menu. Excellent service and incredibly delicious food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6bhzPzBAEoIHnsPVtskZbXCi2CjYn8nUZRuXr&fid=0x0:0x68ebc9aff9d9b505"],"When":"2024-6-23"}]

[{"Name":"Sky Eyes Video","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2JXXl5yK-thMqk8EUNl3FWmyw5SFqlc_KvzAMt-0MdDn-UuKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We always have a great time at the River‚Äôs Reach Pub. They‚Äôve renovated since the last time we were here and everything looks really nice and updated. Both our server and bartender were super attentive and friendly. On one night we came for dinner and had chicken strips and fries (not pictured, because we ate them too fast!).

On our second night we came in just for a few drinks at the bar! We really liked the Spicy Lime Margarita and the Zero Proof Heineken. Definitely the best non-alcoholic beer we‚Äôve tried, tastes just like the real thing. We‚Äôll definitely be back when we‚Äôre in town! Check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsQpGUyuQwqzHNb3UIx_YurZzPJVvGc-R7ONNK&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There were a few things that left room for improvement. The drinks, including the Old Fashioned, were served in plastic cups, which felt a bit out of place for a sit-down pub experience. The chocolate peanut cake was unfortunately stale and overly sweet, as was the coleslaw.

On the bright side, the smashed burger and fish and chips were solidly average ‚Äî nothing mind-blowing but satisfying enough. Overall, it‚Äôs a decent spot for a pub.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEkgw30iit-JywxVTtkfnCgL988HvJ2e6gTFNc&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Carmen Aboytes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCCLFKJlS62-34BUpujZzDsaZV9yysTxPBmk8fhCY7OoETeMyS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A decent spot to grab a quick bite if you're in the area. The pizzas and burgers are fairly good, but I opted for a bowl, and the portion size was disappointingly small. I ended up having to order something else to feel satisfied. If you're looking for a light meal, it might work, but for heartier appetites, you may need to explore other options or order additional items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaknz9FbPkJUiC6a1IlqgOJuBE62sZxQ22ToPP&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"P G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJSQy-hEJFpR-6M_rhWQtV4ho3OA5uBTDPVIdU7lH_VajQsEDm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited The River Reach in New Westminster for brunch, and it was an outstanding experience from start to finish! The new brunch menu is impressive ‚Äî the dish I enjoyed featured crispy bacon, perfectly seasoned potatoes, and the most delicious poached eggs. The flavors were spot on, and the presentation was as appealing as the taste.

What made the experience even more memorable was our server, Lexi, who is hands down the best in New West! Lexi's warm personality, attention to detail, and impeccable service made us feel right at home. She truly went above and beyond to ensure we had a fantastic meal, making our visit even more special.

The River Reach has nailed it with their new brunch offering, combined with the exceptional service from Lexi. If you're looking for a top-notch brunch spot in New West, this is the place to be. Highly recommend, and we will definitely be back! [{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place to come with friends for a bite. We ordered a couple of appetizers and main dishes. I enjoyed the ‚Äúbest fries ever‚Äù dish as it was quite flavourful. We also ordered nachos and thought it was average.

I ordered the fish and chip for my main and I thought it was average as well, can‚Äôt really mess up fish and chips! We also ordered the cookie jar cheesecake and the brownie and I definitely enjoyed the brownie dessert more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpJfMSnZbmGSAtOuJfsPlOBebm5A3RtY3Ep9gl&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Ju","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2D3S_u34v_pqpi-TAMe_IIQ9c28OYIl0iqN7ewQuPCIydQdyDuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went with my kids for the first time today, and it was awesome! The staff were super friendly and made us feel so welcome, especially our birthday boy. Our server Gui was great, made sure that our glasses were always full, gave us some great menu suggestions, and everything came out fast and delicious. The kids loved their meals, and I got to actually relax and enjoy mine.
All in all, very happy, definitely coming back. Thanks again Gui for making his day special!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edward Desaulniers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoP1wTU2-qZu4-kyQmMbasgYbLJv8tKfq6HxU12Zm-ypnqVMIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Like that friend who never lets you down but rarely surprises you either, Browns Social House delivers exactly what you'd expect from a modern casual chain ‚Äì no more, no less. Stopping in an hour before closing on a weekday, we found the familiar comfort of a well-oiled machine running on cruise control, but we felt like the staff was getting ready to leave.

The nachos arrived as they always do ‚Äì adequately portioned, properly layered, neither inspiring poetry nor causing complaint. They're the kind of nachos that make you think, "Yep, those are nachos alright." The drinks followed the same path of calculated adequacy ‚Äì they'll get the job done, but they won't make you forget your favorite cocktail bar.

Where Browns does shine is in its consistency. It's like that old sweater you keep coming back to ‚Äì not because it's spectacular, but because you know exactly what you're getting. The patio offers a pleasant escape, and the service maintains that professional warmth that's become the chain's signature.

This Browns Social House isn't trying to reinvent the wheel ‚Äì they're just keeping it reliably rolling. For a casual meet-up with friends, whether it's lunch, dinner, or late-night bites, it's a safe bet. You won't walk away with a story to tell, but you won't walk away disappointed either.  FYI, the late night Happy Hour is a good value.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Mutadi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGSEocPQRhojQVtaGAuDTqmG1sDbHNEX-Qcv2iO6jQqf5vEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were here after a long day at the hospital. We were a group of nursing students and instructor. I asked our server if I could gift my companions by paying part of their bill and the manager and server went out of their way to make this happen. Everyone loved their food. Drinks were great. Our large group was seated right away. Server was attentive and lovely. Thanks Browns for a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice patio, decent service, and we‚Äôve come to this chain often (for lunch, dinner or late night drinks/appies) and haven‚Äôt ever been dissatisfied with anything. It‚Äôs consistently good.  We tried brunch for the first time and it also was good. Solid chain restaurant that is consistent as expected.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_pkdKS7YmDL5dGe5B4aNMC9NmfygtZ9pAnkW4&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Vero Vero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJqM6z3NvGgp8fOHPNYXy_sxK1l4a3Acl0A1wGDJ4i1AfuQXig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place to enjoy with friends!üòé
Calamari was crispy and delicious. I like the deep fried jalape√±os with calamari. Chicken lettuce wrap was not really impressive. I tried Cactus club one and that one was much much better.. both taste and portion. But still not too bad. Alfredo fettuccine was okay, but maybe if it was more creamy, it would be better. Fish taco was the best among what we ordered. Toppings were all fresh and the portion was great. Deep fried fish stick was super crispy and there was no bad smell. And it came with French fries. (* we ordered an extra fish taco for friends. That is why ours is 3 tacos). Next time I will try happy hour ! No wonder Browns Socialhouse is everywhereüòä","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzK1tp4BoGHjTbQX4Baffg8ca3PcifGn7fB_8e&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2022-1-28"},{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They had a covered patio and we were able to get a seat right away for lunch. Everything was delicious. The nachos was great, I had the potato crusted cod with cowboy salad. The salad was fresh and hint of sweetness. The beef dip was amazing as well. Will come back because it wasn‚Äôt busy at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnkhW3JAKURHPaOApBnp7xuIc5f7mrpLgzylVI&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2021-4-21"},{"Name":"Cynthia Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICUBRND6v4jdjd62BXfRMAYoNx4reXnrOnSeKx6kAQJoR74g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We went to the New West restaurant. We go about 1x every 2 to 3 weeks. I love going there! The food is good, the music playlist rocks and the servers are friendly. They usually make the most tastiest, well built Loaded nachos compared to  other places. This is our go-to for amazing nachos!
But today was a MISS. It was built ok but the taste....none or very little spices...taco seasoning. And it was cold in some spots and warm in others. NOT as impressing as the last 5 to 6x we have been there. The lettuce wraps....that was off too. Very little chicken and on the" dry" side for the sauce. BUT the partner's eggs Benny was good. it was a disappointment for me because I love nachos and lettuce wrap. Will go again in a few weeks for nachos and hope it will be back up to par.  And I will Order the chicken burger.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you haven‚Äôt tried their value breakfast items it‚Äôs worth it. Right now they have 2for4.
Basically choose 2 breakfast items for the price of $4.

On their app you can even modify your order.
Great value thanks Wendy‚Äôs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyyFEnQarAIJsVgivQZJixYIwq3G_XKAT9-Bvm&fid=0x0:0x68cb9877285ae45f"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Aaron Morin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXC8TrYA9mFbAROU7x702Gc8i1QHi-2rkaFkqlT9a1UQkgemw6kg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This location is extremely hit or miss. I always order the same thing, a classic chicken sandwich combo with diet Coke. 50% of the time the sandwich tastes great the fries are hot and salty and the diet coke is perfectly mixed. The customer service is great and served with compassion and a smile. The other half of the time this location misses the mark on food heat, food quality (fries are not salted, diet Coke is pretty much just dark water, and chicken sandwich is old) and the service is impersonal or rude. My advice to management would be quality control across the board.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elie Khoueiry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5oURLERNdcm9BvIr3fAC4qFZbtajTkrn7lvmppBB64F0YQgE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food takes a long time to be ready. This is supposed to be ready fast. Several employees are super slow and wasting time. Check my photos. I asked extra mayo and extra ketchup for the classic burger. They didnt place any ketchup at all and mayo was barely placed. The bacon deluxe didnt have also extra ketchup or mayo and no bacon at all as my photo shows. They're playing tricks to cut down costs and they wouldn't acknowledge their mistakes if you faced them (indians are great in denial). I strongly dont recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqAF3DBbtCOTfUpzuckaCO7hH404-ZKcX6GzDi&fid=0x0:0x68cb9877285ae45f"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"sk Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8_OyuLsneZiK6rhZzsnZBnzEouulBx37JztW7csWW6IqGxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good food and friendly staffs. Coffee is good too. They have a big soft drink machine that customers can choose what drinks they want. I  only take iced water though as I found these drinks are too sweet. This fast food restaurant has baked potato on the menu and is prepared very nicely. I order with sour cream and is a good combination. Their chilli is also very good, tasty and healthy. Chilli not spicy. I like the place and would return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pedro Arteaga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPvNWNlgJG7b336Ym6fr2wEW5sj_ddrmBeQvXXBCdHGyPrKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Overcharged me for my food, manager was extremely rude when I complaint and kept talking with other employees about me in their native language. Did not offer a discount or compensation of any type. Chicken strips are a joke for the price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNluvsvERR0-YE1--XgX1F68UGM8wEBAtSAN5ds&fid=0x0:0x68cb9877285ae45f"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Reza Mansouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTdK2hm81HGTtthigh7khA1UvxR-CdRQr4JJHDCJnKAK5hDeweGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It's really one of the best experiences of eating a burger at Wendy's. This amount of indifference to the brand is really very strange and I can't understand why if it really doesn't matter to you. You can find a Wendy's sign on top of any supermarket. And install, really, when you enter the environment of Wendy's stores, one of the worst things you will encounter is poor ventilation And the terrible smell of meat and fat that fills the air, which makes all your clothes smell quickly and you don't enjoy eating. You can't find anything interesting in this brand, it really needs to be reviewed Training, personnel, environment, ventilation, menu revision, is there really anything as quality control in this brand?What does the marketing team do, does someone really go to the branches as a supervisor? There are many other questions that should be asked","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM1DIUKJWKodRbT78b3SkK0gAfbHHu87wnKoH0fjBIm7ThDUe2VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I orders a large poutine and they didn't put cheese or gravy on it....
When I called to inform them of the mistake they told me I asked for it that way. Why would I spend more ordering a poutine without gravy/cheese instead of just ordering regular fries.....wtf.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3OjyDHBJRR6pEONoflgfKMnHFYQ3lRMq5zQOM3ABOrOdV4ODceQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you feel like throwing 20 bucks away on a couple rotten salads this is your place to go! Ordered a taco salad and the chicken avocado salad and both were full of rotten lettuce.  Into the trash my money goes. Never had this issue at the Richmond location.  I won't be back to this one in New West.  Staff needs to pay more attention.  All they had to do was look at the bottom of the container to see it was had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO387A3fuc085GdMlwN_AHKOKcJC6_T7RfMm8U5&fid=0x0:0x68cb9877285ae45f"],"When":"2022-3-15"}]

Standard Vancouver pricing these days at $15.50-$16 a bowl.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVds4yLV76B9Egpp-pDOZMGXsvc6mntjZN6Pr1&fid=0x0:0xf8174b009e5cfd14"],"When":"2022-9-21"},{"Name":"Arvin Tirk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYh2FT5cCPc0ARnWSgClckRe_ibZeJioJnK0VkkynD8VXZilEl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Honestly a good Vietnamese restaurant with good flavorful dishes and well spaced seating, but then why four stars?

[{"Name":"Regine Aragon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKJwfF8kCTrctxyjmRXYzpqQhsFMeyiHCRIOVgnwQwo-P8I_I7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's so good! Generous serving size, great customer service. üôå

I've been living in the area for almost 2 years. I can't believe it took me this long to try this place. Definitely adding it to my regular New West eats.

Just wish they had more space for seats.

*Note: photo is of a regular chicken shawarma platter","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqlCqJB8cl_GFob-7vSwj8Os20pDjPF3uFaAtM&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Clara Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoMWRC0cDGP4nCpQ1_Zdm86daXS0A0KJbVAa9QczqqbfD7fWIZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were told by friends that this place had really delicious platters and it was an amazing experience! It was our first time here and decided that we couldn't go wrong with the "special platter" which had chicken, lamb, and falafels. We noticed right away that the falafels were made fresh to order and was still crispy by the time we got home (we did take out as there are only 3-4 seats at the front). Beside the fryer was a large pot of fresh rice sitting on the stove as well. For salad you can choose to have a little bit of everything (lettuce, pickled beets, cucumbers, tomatoes, tabouli, pickled red onions, and pickles). They had hummus and tzatziki sauce as options and after the meat was piled on you are also given more sauce options (hot sauce and tahini). They also offer pita to compliment your meal (great with the sauces). This platter was enough to feed two and we'll definitely be back again to try the desserts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK6DRK4bxWIOiSF65jJ0IFzYy5FOI9ASwAnUWY&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Reimun Shleimun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJu0ZwA_4D35g6GEfkag5GeVQ67VwDP2OSszt_p0L2T_fRSmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time in! Was delicious‚Ä¶ Me and wife had chicken wrap, and also tried falafels and rice with chicken. Was amazing every bite. Chicken was Very tender and juicy! Falafels were delicious as well. You can tell freshness by what was offered. Will definitely be back when in the area. Atmosphere and service was great as well! Ty guys, keep it up :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKW5w42WrvL7_LF1bl9N7ZUyRWQELQB94sf_qh&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Mohammed Yahya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLT1QQjsQL0cVBO4YH4tgQfBRBthb4gM79UjFdzAIKyKZVPkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I tried theirs regular size chicken wrap. The size and chicken portion was good 4/5. Cleaning 5/5. One thing i didn‚Äôt like is the service. Poor service 2/5. Everything was ok. There were not many customers around 1pm on Saturday, guess the hype is over? We had prawn fettuccine, chicken wings, mozzarella sticks (not very tasty), and beef penne which was made wrongly, as there's no beef üòÇ they decided to give a discount of $4 for that. My peach bellini was tasty, I like it. There was room to improve service, no water was offered. Without the benefit of that location, I don't think I would return to use that service at that price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMV6TrwhLRKRodlRfiaSHWxtwMw_A8tShYYhFAJ&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Kevin Needham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW091KnP2Cr4T7TVe2u7UM8j8scer3C7OU4HkskIF9bkg_mmAas=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food quality was way above expected. I‚Äôm a new west person and like many adored the patio of old. No changes inside. Would love to see changes there to solidify this place as a year round draw.

What we ate:
Fettuncine ai gamberetti = Pesto cream based with seafood. So good great taste, very fresh, would 100% get again. Affordable relative to what‚Äôs around NW and crave worthy.

Pasta con Filetto di Manzo = tomato based with beef chunks, mushrooms. Also super flavourful, a close second and order-again worthy. Beef was a little tough but not enough to ruin.

Toast skagen = unique fun and light, sauce heavy. Dilly creamy with full prawns. Would order again but more polarizing than other dishes.

Fries = unique, good when hot. Maybe a bit undercooked but I really enjoyed them. Friends said they were a bit sweet.

Drinks:
Old fashioned = great
Itilia fashioned = gorgeous presentation, tasty and what you want from a alcohol forward gin-based grapefruit drink

Apparently more pub favourites to come which I think is a needed guilty pleasure of the residents and this locale. Not available at the time of this review.

Overall seems like management and stuff care. Growing pains like always but good first  impression.

Verdict: Eat New West needs to chill out, give it a chance","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVT32IIw7xw_uSUr1CMq6px5_k4fQI6shUhX-6&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Akhtar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPe1cXkOxnt5e1kl7DXOVX1TkTwivQgahK_8RtarhociYnQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I noticed this new restaurant open up and gave it a try, it exceeded my expectations. I recently visited the Pizza Pizza store in New Westminster and was pleasantly surprised by the excellent customer service I received from Dhyani. She was incredibly friendly, welcoming, and made the experience so much better. Not only did she take my order efficiently, but she also made great recommendations that suited my preferences perfectly.

The pizza was fresh, delicious, and exactly as ordered. It‚Äôs rare to find such a great combination of tasty food and exceptional service, but Dhyani made it happen! I‚Äôll definitely be coming back, thanks to her warm and professional approach. Highly recommend this location and be sure to ask for Dhyani when you're there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQJpbDXFgQjpMv8u0Bed2Dq8c_OpbOIhPT7oY&fid=0x0:0x3dc7ae0d353627e2"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Josephine Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4ctBP8R2rm9S8Aa5NyuULMapTvyTQYakS6AvI9Cd025oSy86H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza had a deal where you could get 4 small 1 topping pizzas for $20, so my husband decided to take advantage of the deal.

The first time we tried Pizza Pizza was when they opened up a shop in New Westminster. We loved their pizza and ordered it many times.

Eventually a shop opened up closer to us, in Burnaby but we tried it twice and were quite disappointed with it.

When my husband saw this deal for the 1 topping pizzas, he decided to try ordering from the shop in New Westminster that we use to always order from before the one in Burnaby had opened.

Good call! It turns out, it's just that Burnaby location that's not up to par. The one we originally used to order from in New Westminster still makes excellent pizza. We'll only be ordering from that location from now on. Not going back to the Pizza Pizza in Burnaby ever again!

Service: Good

The food was absolutely delicious‚Äîeach bite of the pizza was perfectly cooked with fresh, high-quality ingredients. The variety of toppings and the unique flavor combinations were impressive. What truly stood out was the customer service; the staff was incredibly friendly and attentive, making sure every detail was perfect. I highly recommend this Store to anyone looking for top-notch pizza and a great dining experience. I'll definitely be coming back here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ganesh Kale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEJPxBdv0ynGu8yBGFDtHHpcWu3psVF1RoCQy-PpzZGUyEuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"i ordered 3 (1-extra large  and 2 large pizza on Friday and i received worst pizza i ever seen. mushroom and broccoli are almost half burn.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvSypyO1d_LKq5wDIxXgOjhafx3YMhdJ2YZ6Z0&fid=0x0:0x3dc7ae0d353627e2"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Jas Dhesi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQvfDH7uSMCEzro-CsN6IwB-0jOA8mYgacjQA_vQrRm_jz8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered pizza when I went to the store, the Girl at the  front was very friendly . The service was great and quick . very clean pizza store . Sat there with my kids to eat . I ordered chicken pizza , chicken tenders and wings. Food Tasted delicious. I recommend this pizza place .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Yousefi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQzNzY381-LWZEW-4YXqIwPWrNQXPQ2m75gH06nD0MtRhU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The staff‚Äôs behavior was not good at all. They were not professional. They started talking their own language in front of us.
They didn‚Äôt use gloves or hairnets.
The restaurant was very cold.
Any request we had was rejected. We asked for ketchup, and they said they didn‚Äôt have any. We had to swipe our card twice because it couldn‚Äôt be processed in a single transaction. I asked them to put all the pizza slices in one box, but they refused. Instead, they stacked two slices on top of each other.

It was not a good experience, and I absolutely not recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY2HjShvQ_Cz09JqW0fv681DLjqachewnX3uVSlkf5Ee09RKZS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"*****BE CAREFUL WHEN PAYING!!!
My family usually order pizza from here, last time my father went to pick up 2 M pizza 2 toppings $9 dollar each,  the lady in the till had the debit machine ready to tap, when my father got in the car he noticed that this worker added $5 dollar tip without asking!! My understanding is that tips are OPTIONAL!!! I felt concerned about this as I think she took advantage of my senior dad","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sally Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWRytNEd3rFUQ5nqN3VotbBVQY7R-XLnx2acb4glkPd-K-gSTD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"**BUYER BEWARE**

There is a deal advertised on their website - $11.99 for a large 1-topping pizza. We have used this deal multiple times in-person. When I ordered a large pepperoni pizza at the store the other day, I was charged regular price. I paid, thinking the deal must no longer exist. However, sure enough, the deal was still there when I checked online. When I went to pick up the pizza, I asked and the employee said that the deal is ‚Äúonline only‚Äù.

When I got home, we read the fine print and it did not indicate anywhere that this special is ‚Äúonline only‚Äù. My husband went back to the store to confirm and the employee tried to argue that I had ordered the ‚Äúrecipe pizza‚Äù. Eventually they admitted that you CAN get the pepperoni pizza with the special so there was no reason to charge regular price for it, especially since I had referenced the special.  Eventually, my husband was given a $5 refund (the total difference was $5.65 lol. Oh well, by now, the amount we were owed was no longer the point).

All that to say, if the employee had charged me the regular price by mistake, I wouldn‚Äôt be mad. But to lie and say the special was ‚Äúonline only‚Äù to avoid honouring the deal is pretty scummy.

An email to their corporate office did not yield anything besides a scripted apology and response saying they will forward this to the appropriate team to address with the individuals involved.

All in all, pretty disappointed that none of the Pizza Pizza representatives proactively tried to make this right. We will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

No tax for the holiday!!!
Not all heroes wear capes and when you Try their food you‚Äôll see what I mean. I highly recommend the super chicken lamb combo and just tell him make it the way they‚Äôd make it for themselves.!!!

You guys rock
Nick Conville

We highly recommend El Santo for a fun and romantic evening out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkT8EmXcTzgAFww4IqHdYHds65_KcYK6Ej0Von\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Amanda Ballantyne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_5vlj7yXUGy_6pMA2oPSW0Ema7d32lk4ZVKgwLnF8pOgeHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful experience here yesterday. We were headed to a show so needed an early dinner and decided to try out the happy hour at a favourite of ours, El Santo. We moved out of New West a year ago but try to get back to this gem when we can. We parked at the Columbia skytrain station and it‚Äôs just a 2 minute walk from there. From the minute we stepped through the doors we were greeted warmly and provided with friendly, knowledgeable service from the wonderful staff. We decided to do tapas style so we could sample more items and had the trio of salsas with their homemade tortilla chips, a trio of tacos, the best brussel sprouts ever and the cornbread with jalape√±o jelly. Every bite was just perfection and we left stuffed! My only regret was that I was too full to get some of their churros for dessert‚Ä¶I dream about those things‚Ä¶sigh. Also, their margaritas are the best in the business. Seriously, you must try one. It was another great visit and there will be many more to come!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ8vf5MxY9NvVXqT2JWy_P0GGaR3iAGfHVgrk5\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Thomas Wilczynski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJD24Or0RUBGSuMLrdcePCdBXv8sl7ZLUknVBIS-JYZ_nACiVt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This restaurant is excellent! Sophisticated vibes and an impressive menu. The chicken empanadas were perfect. Now, it is an upscale dining experience, so prices are higher and quantity is lower. If this is your style, then I totally recommend El Santo. But, my family and friends wouldn't enjoy this so much. I just went here solo to celebrate the day after my birthday, and I had no regrets.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPI24atQLYD_a0X0w6Jh1s1MjvoEZnGt7xWFbdu\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Jessie Kenk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHO7_squ4YXAxgK5UNOjY9caZDzSTUhThfzCKeZMd7_ZDrAuM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"El Santo is a cute little restaurant a super close walk from the New West Skytrain station. Went on a Sunday evening and they were able to accommodate my party of 6. The restaurant lighting had a moody ambiance but a super lively atmosphere. The host and the waitstaff provided excellent service. Everyone loved their drinks both the alcoholic cocktails and zero-proof. I ordered the burrata and it was delicious I loved the tart marmalade. The pescaco taco was a hearty helping size the fish and the toppings were super fresh. Other dishes of note were the guacamole trio, empanadas, and definitely get the churros for dessert they are fried perfectly!! Overall the quality of the food is worth the price pull definitely recommended as a date night, as an outing for a special occasion or just if you're craving delicious Mexican food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEOCerU6c6cS0Knw3TyKAtBfiYOhgb_ml3nrXY\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Oluwayomi Adebule","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXqcIg8ujO4XiC50cD8_FM6q8RuvnCHkeqVI4f08BodMBvibbJTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambience was ok. The food portions were quite small and you need to order more than one dish for fulfillment. As it was brunch, the menu was very limited. The drinks were cool and they offered to fix the overly limey taste of the mangonada. It‚Äôs an ok choice for brunch if you‚Äôre in the New Westminster area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXm3-kUfykxZ6OvDYhrG5fYaAP8XFpXjW71zzF\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Harrison K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyo531Mh7oStmPsGBaM8AJF3i5eACQbjfzoajBXrYo2AJFczKXPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to El Santo a few times. The main dishes options for dinner I don‚Äôt like much. Their prices are reasonable as well. Overall, it's a great spot for a satisfying meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5hV6Lbgr50Qfe8skvqBzFzRi68iXmv5E-ih5Y&fid=0x0:0x7b4a774892ebfabe"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Erik Hiebert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjbFtFKvIRMnXecf6zUz1-wrrAyMj6Z_gE3CFM2LPzGilV9mdT1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The service is always very good & friendly here, but I'm disappointed with the quality of the food. It's fine if you just want a quick batch of pancakes from their classic pancake mix but when branching into other parts of their menu I've been disappointed by the ingredients and the quality of the cooking.

Recently tried their avocado toast with medium poached eggs - advertised to have grilled bread, avocado and roasted cherry tomatoes. The bread was just a plain piece of Dempsters or something, not grilled in the pan nor toasted for more than 10 seconds, the cherry tomatoes were raw with some blackened edges, probably thrown in a very hot pan for 10 seconds. The eggs were hard poached with the whites totally falling apart and swimming in a pool of water. Really disappointing. The eggs also seem to be the cheapest kind of eggs (not free range) based on the very bright yolk colour and lack of richness of the yolk.

I've found the omelettes also dont have much egg flavour - I suspect both due to them using cheap eggs and using a bit of pancake mix in the omelette to give it the fluffiness, resulting in the egg tasting a bit bland, so it relies on the cheese and other toppings to carry it in the flavour department. But they are a generous portion size for the price.

I also noticed plastic is chipping/shredding off the spout of the coffee carafes so I'm hoping there arent little bits of plastic melting off into my coffee as I pour... Think these might need to be replaced with ones that dont use a plastic spout.

I'll stick to pancakes and waffles from here on out if I go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUKzUgqHy8jSvG0JurXp1bAJ4CpzGpaELXQMuW&fid=0x0:0x7b4a774892ebfabe"],"When":"2024-7-7"}]

[{"Name":"Gen X Surrey Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnz98iwXPE1DskfLpfNg-zDV5mDy1tGmvmbNcHWdRqf6q4OTmNvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good food. Good service. The char sui protein add-on was pretty gnarly. I wouldn't recommend that. But the Bombay mac and cheese was excellent.

I ordered medium hot but the server warned against it. He said he'd give me some hot sauce on the side that I could add in if I liked. He didn't think I'd like the heat level. I appreciated the advice. It wasn't too hot but I like that he cared enough to mention it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp6lQFWAUK-GmbFqVshtnkXdFOIk9pv_ezO7wT&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Aarna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyKiPt9xTa8ZNQM2KUPVsXHP40b2Zu4rW1CyCzcZ5rQDcsYM8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for brunch with my mom, we ordered the spicy peanut coconut box, kids mac and cheese (we got some spice added) and chicken bites. The spicy peanut box was 10/10, amazing. Flavour was spot on and so was the spice it was packed with veggies and we both loved it. The mac and cheese sauce was not thick, very cheesy and spicy because we got some added. This was probably one of the best mac and cheese i‚Äôve have in the area. The chicken bites were well coated however there wasn‚Äôt much flavour in them so I wouldn‚Äôt recommend unless it‚Äôs for children. The service WAS quick, the bites arrived before my mom even settled down after ordering and the boxes arrived 5-7 minutes after that. Overall good experience, I would recommend noodle box!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk2re0WVUDNIrUQe0soobkkfHebMl9Rhnu0BWY&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Hemant Saini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnmX5eLp24nybXuyZKU4sp5QN8w1CUMmnlsJvpw07_6Eo0ghWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Noodle Box can't be termed as a classic Asian Cuisine restaurant chain. At best, it's Asian influenced fusion food.

Having sampled 5 dishes - I think this chain offers some delicious concoctions to try out.

The food presentation was pretty good and value for money.

I had ordered my serve Schorching Hot and was supposed to feature Ghost Peppers but it was more of some kind of BBQ sauce poured without restraint.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQG8c6t7gVFOZujskLQCim3r8mKmuRA_YxrRyj&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Alberto Galleguillos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKT_Q6hbseR7v-tM50X6qEUnu3mVTWAX810Jeq_5U6UQFoucA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered thai chow mein 2 weeks ago and paid extra for crispy chicken.  When I got home, there was no chicken.  I emailed New West noodle box the next day, but did not receive a response until later in the week when I included the corporate email.  It then took an additional week for the manager to ask for my email (via email...) for an etransfer for the refund.  I received the refund a few days later for an unusual amount (more than the cost of the chicken, but less than the meal), and NO NOTE to confirm it was for the refund/inconvenience.

Granted, its a small/insignificant error/issue, but if this is how they respond to simple errors, I am afraid if there are more serious issues (allergies? [{"Name":"Austin Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNDFlFRW448NsW9Ue-ITcpTpPH-MPu5nnuyforeJZCgfBQ3Hk1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently got takeout at the Boston pizza new west location.
The server was nice. However, I asked for nothing to be added but I believe I was charged for cheese which wasn‚Äôt a big deal.
The problem was that the size of the takeout pasta was less than half of other Boston pizzas I have been to. I was still hungry after finishing this $20 pasta (on pasta Tuesday).
I‚Äôm not sure why this location gives so much less, I do not recommend take out at this location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVNe0LrtjbTXP4kFyzmvuYjy8EbyfmNMJQI_p0&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Harman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6uc1ezaDNXGFJdzjR6BUuoqdE4wrH6Rbo83DtVXeSJdUqzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We went in around 2 pm. Host sat us on our table and told us server is coming. Guess what no one came for good 15 minutes then host himself took our order and messed it and never got our drink. Wonderful lunch i guess.

I have filled all the info u asked for. I am expecting a call back from you guys. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmlKfUaSKDuLpM09Y-K1zltGbMS0UMDxbf6ZaC&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Kimberly W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyEcFWm9KlF1A5qUr48_2k5NqNkBKB28_JBHp8Hk3SydvKzo4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had a work group dinner here and while I didn‚Äôt mind the food, the service we received here was some of the worst service I‚Äôve ever experienced. We had a server named Hussain and he was extremely rude to us. First off, when we arrived, he never clearly stated when he would be taking our orders. He would just stand in a corner with his notepad thinking that we could read his mind. We did have a few people in our party that were more vocal than others so they made their orders known, but then he would openly roll his eyes at them for making many requests. For people like me who would quietly wait for a server to approach and ask us for our order, he would never do that because he would stand SO far away from our table and just walk away if no one directly called for him. I shouldn‚Äôt have to yell that I want something from across the room. He also brought our drink orders incorrectly so I‚Äôm not even sure if he heard us properly since we had to yell across the room to order. When he finally did come to take our individual orders, he crouched at the corner of our table and didn‚Äôt move individually to each person so the person at the far end of the table didn‚Äôt hear when it was her turn. When he was waiting for her order he just shouted, ‚Äúum excuse me, HELLO‚Äù but she didn‚Äôt see him as he was crouched and far away since it was a long rectangular table. When we asked for water, he brought a pitcher but left it on a completely different table far away (we were in a special group room) and so we had to get up ourselves and bring the pitcher and cups to our table (for reference, our table didn‚Äôt even have food on it yet so it was clear). He took forever in between orders and gave us attitude with every interaction. Luckily however, he only took our orders. A different lady brought all our food and was super sweet and accommodating for the rest of our requests when we asked for takeout containers and other things. She was extremely tall, her hair was in dreadlocks, and wore glasses. I wish we received service with her the entire time instead of our other server Hussain.

The food itself was pretty decent, I ordered the ribs and they weren‚Äôt dry at all, but the service we received definitely took away from the experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_O8zT5bIGOhyatx-4AVTl5IKG71o6-Q-u132X&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Danielle Bertsch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdkmuiv2cRnHyHhY_fQK5g3Rx7POQeI0iZN-dw6fgHHp6ZaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their happy hour menu is always a great value. Happy to see lots of yummy food other than pasta & pizza (although I love them too)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqYqhv1k9du0SibbbVJ2OzWhOSXt8Y80Pxg1yf&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"shannon radonjic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6BVT0mKqO1z-7XYCNxE-qt6Wcet3T21CTbGjrvOlcYUFJBzb3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered take out.
Asked for a Thai Chicken Wrap with easy sauce and it was literally a sauce wrap.  3 little pieces of chicken, barely any even lettuce. Soggy, disgusting mess.
Also ordered my kid a kids meal and the cookie was open.
I called in to let them know and I was told there is nothing they can do about it and the guy put the phone down so I could listen to the kitchen staff.
No offer to remake, or even a sorry.
They really value customers.

Other locations are great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfCn8r2_ZKf9wFhwYC1LRIHaOzNjzrCcQLC8U0&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-3-8"},{"Name":"Craig Reichel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYE33sokWFBv5iyf2C6-cYdDuArJfIyefzcfI5AzrlKhOyvF0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Friendly service, ok food, in desperate need of a deep cleaning. The place is kind of dirty and run down inside, but the service was fine and the food passable. Nothing special it is a decent place to have a beer, pizza, and watch hockey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2kv9_B1uWnnwbRHaZDqdPwtrDRAtZc-Njdrif&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-3-11"},{"Name":"MJP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKls-GtZ_q1FjietaWcx0agpc7H1nUcOmFI23Yn3SpVd3GCITdK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pasta Tuesday is a must while happy hour, more affordable and decent price. It wasn't busy at all either. Would definitely come back üôÇ. Our total was only $62 for all of this which was a good deal to me! üôÇ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK8rohUDUGmDoSdlsH9fuIp-rI3-PwBWeCr_dc&fid=0x0:0x99e6edd948ed2527"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"Sagar Ghevde","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUitU8STg7kqtTuY_zwHZI-IFfb4KvcO243KQ80Dr3LIfwA4snmgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boston Pizza (New Westminster)
Good spot for a casual meal with friends or family. The menu is diverse, and the pizza is flavorful and fresh. The atmosphere is relaxed and welcoming. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jesse Short","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_QnK6aCuRyloJkdMhF6-7Z4djVnpJZpfP8W46czbb57mXpyb7dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The service and atmosphere was nice, The beers were well priced, The food was really the only issue.

To say that this was pub, food is stretching it, I ordered nachos, wings and a chicken burger.

The wings were tiny, overcooked, very little meat on them, extremely disappointed.

The nachos, The top layer had some cheese, but 90% of the dish was me dipping dry chips into salsa. The $3 guacamole add was terrible In flavor and portion size, assuming it was squeezed out of a tube, I managed 6 moderate dips before it was exhausted.

The chicken burger actually was pretty good, I was surprised, and if I did happen to return it would likely be the food I would order just because It at least was satisfying.

I watched four other orders of nachos come out and all appeared to be approximately the same subpar quality.

Do yourself a favor and go for cheap drinks and go anywhere else for food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQ9ahN2E8LjKURfs2X7wJXD-ZvixWFfWF-kLWb&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Gavin Sawle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKXhLvSjLukpWbwISwzG_LZo19X4tY7GMRNFiHyB4E59XSvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A HUGE shout out to the Terminal Pub last night: we were in a large group for our annual Christmas get together, and the one server we had in particular, was phenomenal. The bar and kitchen staff were great as well, making sure our food and drinks were served as fast as they were ordered.
Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mouse Behave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJljCheKy1R6LD-pnnLdWkCANUS7SejobG8NXgusm9Jl6gs-gU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I did not like this restaurant at all. The location of the restaurant is pretty sketchy at night with rats crawling all over the ground also it is next to a pornography store. The food was very bad and tasted like it was from the freezer and the portions were skimpy. Do not go here at all costs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Proctor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU4reTki5_DKZ68y-D-U91LkDlip7ln3Ocfw5-ZSYEfQqSejCW2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very old watering hole in New Westminster, B.C., Canada. Newish owner and beautifully renovated. Very nice ambiance. Expansive beer menu & great food. Our server Astrid was very pleasant & engaging üçªü•Ç","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNstrj1dB1m7URoScdnNbh2vZIBjErSh9yIhDxK&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2023-3-25"},{"Name":"Doodle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCnlmDZcGE9OF2_ELIGqxTNYZaUi5B2FQYO6pK44e8F6Xq3jyI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy and wonderful atmosphere, food was good. Handmade burger patties, and pretty sure the onion rings are made in house as well. Was surprised at first that I only got like 7 onion rings, but they are deceptively filling and really good.

Kind of farther off from things, which means there is a quieter crowd","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dean Rau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtvbv_2m5DukfoxGm0h-R0KwmwKsEIh2vPZUq-TO1J_DjAcLZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Moe is a charming man. Smooth and cool, quietly deserving respect. Represents the Terminal Pub most proper. The menu was most reasonably priced although my visit was too short to sample all that was offered, I will be back. Quite a nice large natural gas fireplace is a perfect spot for a bite and drinks for two.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzE-lf7sXyTsvQH-VcCT2ZghmyYFgNlEXoDte3&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2023-2-17"},{"Name":"Ling To","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlFxJCKp6bjqARUOXgwrUpHcbKAm9tBpTn_ze63uacIdbffw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dusty and Mohsan are great hosts! The semi-private section of the restaurant was an amazing space for a group gathering. Excellent snacks, well priced drinks and exceptional service! Shall be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeV-qkub-3gdk1BJb-Xohl5aCzUzS3j4fozzHZ&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2022-12-10"},{"Name":"Lakshay Sehgal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3dWzexjPh--uSP5xvFWGSLJ9CkKGzspFPthLs--IkuyjtyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had one of the best times here Jessie and Ryler were one of the best people i have ever met working at a bar very hospitable and i am from Vancouver these guys made me feel comfortable and they were pleasant to
Talk to. Thank you had the best time here.","Images":null,"When":""}]
