[{"Name":"Stacy Bohun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7qzTk0Z_bh312ltTEPQYsTQ_AchFTo1bVXqCNkOxE5OXtj0I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Elisse was my waitress. She was amazing, love her energy and quick service!

Will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCOHTRnSyYNgFFt_82UmoryMXs7gisM61aMRw&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They have extremely expensive wings. It is advertised as 1 pound of wings for $14.95 but they only give you 6 wings (which is most definitely not 1 pound of wings). The wings did taste fine though just very small portions. The calamari was also good but came on a very small plate. Drink specials were good.
The service was excellent. Trivia night on Wednesdays are fun.

Overall great for drinks but expensive food and small portions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpjmcPA2bKzLVxuCdnF7CPGHXvlzTMdk1u0Ud_&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2023-1-20"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited this pub a few times, usually in summer to be seated on
their patio area. It offers quite a decent list of beverages. I found their choice of IPAs to be a bit weak, but after pandemic re-opening, they introduced Mariner IPA to the list, and it's a game-changer for me. Service is slow at times, mainly because the place is packed, and there's only one waitress, but it's bearable. We never went past appetizers, but I can tell that wings are good, and mozzarella triangles are nice when cheese stays inside, which doesn't happen always, and you get triangles with no cheese inside. Also, I'm not sure if it's a post-pandemic measure, but now the kitchen closes at 8 pm. For us, somehow missing the last kitchen call, it was the end of the night. One other thing that I really liked, which is not available anymore in COVID-19 reality for very obvious reasons, is that they used to have a popcorn machine where patrons could get a free popcorn ‚Äì it's genius. I can't say that this pub is perfect, but they are trying to be so, and I can see why many locals like it. Give it a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZEqfi9l4WmpCuAoVPlab--oxMV1YFPfQzXgQi&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2020-6-29"},{"Name":"David 04 Make the World a Better Place","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkrAyRsAwad4uDl0EKEwpsCVMLq51IOxmbley55h_iwJzGo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really nice place to drink!
When I went there, it was movie day.
They didnt serve food;; But service was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCoro3kVbx6q0upeAPkj2vFcHskUDIx7khzCA&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2023-7-13"},{"Name":"Sean Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjbgELxR0qim_ljk8eaK8OgzP61UXXAqq-zknTzwLJdAueKkc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like this place. The fact that they have Heineken on tap is a big plus for me, because it's my favourite beer. This place has a great selection of beers on tap. I've never tried the food here, so I don't have an opinion about it. The staff is friendly and I have had nothing but good experiences every time I've come here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Spoke Spurr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6SBXwfGoUXIMfCRHI82vggrz0MEiQ4COzIjzyCQuY_w8CfkTv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We must‚Äôve picked an incredibly poor Saturday afternoon. A dozen lonely, sad men sitting at individual tables. It was as if we walked into Moe‚Äòs Tavern of Simpson fame.
Dreary.
We left.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chowder Head","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwlpI7DoMMgrt2BIfQlFGVP_FkXyOuSIv5tzHDvkSUHslBPM4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My big pet peeve is places that advertise beer special prices that don't include alcohol tax.

$5.45 beer special? 4 of them plus tip ran me over $40. Dirty pool Hops.... Dirty pool..

Service that was completely indifferent.  Thursday just after 9pm kitchen already closed.

It's really close to the skytrain and that's its best feature.

There's superior options to this place within 5 minutes walk.

Really disappointed as I'd seen it there for so long. This was just my experience and with some like this I won't review until I've gone a few times but there's no way I'm ever going back there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Straver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWToLMyoie5tYNi3FxHCGKh7tJbpoBo5POEd0V1juGjM4ChsMJT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New to New West, but come here often for drinks. Never had their food before but their customer service is so great I didn't want to leave a bad impression. Really friendly staff/locals and great prices.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Celina Arenillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPvcNqjpmtihcb5J8miFlC4lw0H-EdaSQUtLM4u3kh0_GMHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had dinner here. The food was great and cheaper as compared to other Indian Restaurants in New Westminster. Service was pleasant.

I think they have to work on their back area where the washroom was, it was unkept and dark, making the washroom look not as clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdsNgkpEQ6TbpZvsQvIghhP9MNUvHErvt28k-9&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Richard Catania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItC6YbJoIIB4dwzioVUZ1DnCoFgM8-BVohNT5avuOwKh7Rhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Poor communication, and lack luster food. Ordered a butter chicken, chicken vindaloo, chicken biryani, and naan. When I got there they had a tandoori chicken instead of the vindaloo. She didn‚Äôt know what vindaloo was. I said I asked if you had vindaloo when I called to order and you said yes. I showed her a picture, she asked the owner I assume and they made a vindaloo.  Food was very oily, and very bland. The butter chicken was not bad and naan was good. The vindaloo was tasteless. No punch of spice nor vinegar. Same with the biryani. Butter chicken and vindaloo did not come with the basmati rice as it was supposed to. I called back when I got home and was told it only comes with curries. What is butter chicken and vindaloo?  Will not order from here again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO85KB_cKwsNNSmmVnlxxzgqbI9jaQxnFo3Ycph&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"discovery sonu ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_b2reRKsjtiT_HffF8-yN5QM1sqqpXd5OaoIUa8-ff3hRWT7Gdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant and had a wonderful experience. The interior decoration is beautiful and creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The staff is incredibly cooperative. And a special mention goes to Mandeep Kaur, who provided exceptional service. She was friendly, professional, she made our dining experience enjoyable üòäüòäüòäOverall, it's a fantastic place to eat, and I highly recommend it to anyone looking for a great meal and excellent service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpFtpUL7UTlXjlxA1DkEvaMjpbHbSXvZFRL4vD&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Johnny G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBbi4rvv-nHDl7H6RXbToA_kk3n9Hj_ierIgyWzQHyZr_63w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The flavours here are amazing. Every dish is fully loaded with deliciousness. I want to try everything here. Very curious what everything tastes like. Fish pakora deal is reasonable and portion is pretty big. The samosas are excellent. Nice and crispy with spice. Non veg combo was pretty solid, pretty filling. Lamb curry and butter chicken was so flavorful. These flavors turned my chicanery filled day into a super positive flavor explosion in my mouth.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMByDw_KPHdSo-oNPXdSWgscX1D-xSQthM4RR2-&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Srikantha Kalaghatta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7kV3vSmU11E2VJr6yMSYBtHLByJ47CPuwfOKoc_5xVBiEfsZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My wife and I went to this restaurant last evening and we both were really hungry. The place is quite modest and there is street parking right in front of the restaurant. The experience at this restaurant didn't start off great! The initial welcome lacked attention from the front desk staff, leaving us to find our own table and later, place our order at the front desk ourselves as no one came to our table to take the order.

We ordered Veg Fried Rice and Channa Batura and both were exceptionally flavorful. However, it took 28 minutes for our order to arrive despite us being the only customers at that time. The tardiness aside, we would certainly be going back here for the tasty food.

The potential of this restaurant lies in its delectable cuisine. With improved service, Indian Courtyard has the potential to offer an excellent dining option in the New Westminster neighborhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFC9cWeuGKfDCbkfs7-dtRsYiOJF_rNZTC0yiM&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"604 Eats","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKydooBZGXt2w5Pplqp4pqyT8VrJYMUXmY8f1v2W9oYs1nCEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food smelled delicious and tasted pretty good.  The price for the portion size is pretty decent.  My coconut curry lamb was amazing, but my friend's chicken Tikka masala was too spicy for her liking.  The veggie pakora was good, but a little dry/overcooked.  The restaurant has a nice ambiance, but I think most of their business is take out as they didn't have wine as a drink selection.  I would come here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxMRE-vTlo4RqDWAIzteLaXsoMW1cAzo5L66QC&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2022-11-15"},{"Name":"Ramin Tahouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3PGFwXhFR5wrjRgqZ8C6g76cQqHMugwCusafBYZgKtQdvNkVR0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came in here with an old buddy to get some late night grub. Food was over all tasty and excellent. Their lamb methi malai was really good. The portion sizes don‚Äôt seem to make much sense. I was a bit disappointed in the portion size being $18 for the main but was served as half the size of a normal full order at any other restaurant you can think of. Their Raita was on the other hand, over portioned. But all in all really good food and service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsMIuqXRQkmmVae-4LjhOtqlGCoX1SKWxOPeaW&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-9-29"},{"Name":"Coleen C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUauoBULHRivIFwYCvu4BqvyF8VvNRVLHo1AYN5p3b5oAIqNmsS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first dining experience here was amazing! I've been hearing good things about this restaurant in FB New West group and this place doesn't disappoint. The flavour definitely hits the spot! I'll definitely go back again to try other things in the menu. I hope they'll add in their menu an option of butter chicken sauce in the samosa someday. I think its a good combination. I highly recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOw6KunyGFNf_P-QFA5WL1aQ8AKDC-tRi8Z9Ap6&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2021-5-28"}]

[{"Name":"Rafael Prato","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmw8x9RDf8apa9mg4sXkmCUBL57rpPrrUqVoRoTSqzlDDkuKry=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"McDonald's in New Westminster is a dependable spot for a quick and satisfying meal. The menu offers all the classics you love, from Big Macs to McNuggets, served quickly and consistently. The friendly staff and clean environment add to the overall positive experience.

Exciting news for fans: the beloved retro sauce is making a comeback! This nostalgic favorite adds an extra layer of flavor to your meal, bringing back fond memories with every bite. Whether you're a longtime fan or new to the taste, it's definitely worth trying.

Overall, McDonald's in New Westminster combines great service, tasty food, and a touch of nostalgia, making it a top choice for fast food in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoYdk4HF5mj4RicZXb1g5jaZh01e7MasC2GGU1&fid=0x0:0x3a93611eb43e48b0"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoVuF5WI-U9TjtfSOKcqTsO5Lw1SS5ttxQgnOeYapUbWYHkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"disgusting service, it feels like the workers are not even trying to make the burger neat, they threw everything in one pile, dirty tables and toilets, do not come here, the wishes for the order do not seem to be taken into account, if I ask without ice, I want a drink where there is no ice, and not where there is as much as the rest of the drinks. I would like to get my $7 back for this delicious burger, I didn't get any pleasure, plus my stomach hurt after this burger, I hope you didn't spit in it for me","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOckC7AwTAgHbasXCU0e6ffUR-kkXd-cXm1_W6x&fid=0x0:0x3a93611eb43e48b0"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Lister Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWbNvO55wOzkDRxCcJ-fMoCcdWyut5hlx-H_zUreRnwso9_V0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoyed their chicken waffle. But would have preferred on muffin. Hash browns nice and crispy. Pomegranate blueberry smoothie was a little too thick. Came back for lunch and had turf and surf. Not bad. French fries not crispy but hash browns this morning were. Passion fruit guava smoothie was delicious but little too thick. This is very clean restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhKOEzEl69bhW52dUnSxVMIZcnl1JMA-51OoBK&fid=0x0:0x3a93611eb43e48b0"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Darcy S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlx_-zwVy0cqsYy9gHOL2-LibNVuOG-4ypo4ZvB11K55XRcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Staff were too busy with drive-through and Skip orders to get counter orders in a timely fashion. It took 35 minutes from ordering to get our food and was a very straightforward order. Moreover, when we asked why the number for our order had been removed, we were told it would be up shortly in a very curt and abrupt fashion. When we finally got our food, there was no apology or acknowledgment of the delay. When we notified McDonald's corporate of our concerns, there was no offer of compensation, just the overdue apology and a mention that the concern would be forwarded to the specific restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMHgpY4gNAcNxsjCJZezquqHjF2-t37wSg--P1LqmEVCp-Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A FAST PACED, exciting experience!! I was dazzled by the fast, friendly service. The staff is truly professional, and tolerant of the sometimes challenging clientele in The Royal City","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzY2IBlsU60XkFK8AU6SNHwxPzUxb9eniybgFIfwbC5mhfjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"During the inflation, good options in budget deal.
I came here to get the Halloween bucket for my kid. However, they did not list that out of stock...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJILlz822hzqEBuBdirVFdUDW0mdm2C7SJtix7&fid=0x0:0x3a93611eb43e48b0"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"paddy man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWaVfMp9z47zJ-G5bq_sgwbXmywwoJfyv2GTnNkxOLQtktFn4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Of all the McDonald's I have gone to, this one is by far the worst for customer service. I rarely get my order in less than 10 minutes and more often than not, the order is wrong. Sometimes I order off the kiosk and find out they don't have what I ordered yet don't remove it from the kiosk. They try to substitute it with something else, more often cheaper than what I ordered and never offered to refund the difference, I had to demand the difference refunded because they were not even going to do it. I had to wait 10 minutes the other day for a small black coffee and the last time I ordered a meal, the just put it on the counter and walked away without calling the order number out. If I dare complain about anything there, I get a face full of attitude, never an apology. McDonald's in general is the worst for value, way too high prices for what you get.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yuki Doshita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJDZAUZ3cKzcxMHFvvdqvIWFGWfY3GlvchJeqpULd5UZbWJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I orderd cheeseburger without buns for takeout. Opened it at home, and there was buns but no patty. I cried a little.
The fries had red paint on some of them too.

Not a good day.

Update: I've reported this on the McD's app since it was a mobile order through the app, they've refunded me 6000pt. I'll come back to get my meat patty I guess. Thank you McD's.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRNZ-vrIXHTJMo6v8q_J-HfbaMKXczD1MKfqba&fid=0x0:0x3a93611eb43e48b0"],"When":"2024-6-20"}]

[{"Name":"Shawn Gale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7ZcqBuTGbnxvR30S4a6N938p_TbyxARKKVRuZFB29uQM13f_Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This tap and bistro blew me away, The Notorious Grey Fox, site of the old BC Penitentiary. My wife and I visited here for the first time last Friday. We were unsure of what to expect, since we'd only seen the location from East Columbia. From that vantage point, it's hard to judge. We caught happy hour before 5pm and enjoyed amazing food. In particular, the chips and salsa, which was next level salsa made in house. Also, always a good indicator of service, the coffee was fresh and in a large cup, which they were quick to refill. I highly recommend visiting here. I know we'll be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9XJQ2PaH7iqt-PPcxNGkue7PjK7ED3wThDY-R&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I've seen many iterations of a pub here, I was hoping this would be better...

Sat on the beautiful balcony, a fair beer selection. I had an IPA and Ma had a white wine...

Looking over the menu we both realized that there really wasn't a wide variety of food here.

I ordered the beef dip in the pepperoni flatbread.

Initially looked good, the bread was crusty but soft still. A little too much of their house horseradish on top. I would have preferred a nice little dish of this on the side so that I could load it at my discretion. The fries were tasty...

Ma, she wasn't impressed at all with the pepperoni flat bread. She said that it was bland and doughy...

I'll keep an eye on the menu, see if anything ever changes there. I wouldn't return for a meal, but I would have a beer there...

It is great they allow üêïüê∂ on their patio!

***Edit***

It's truly unfortunate that this place also replies, without ever really addressing the concerns.

Clearly, the respondent got their feeling hurt in life and they feel the need to be cutting in their replies. My review was an opinion, their response only tells me to not bother looking again at the menu, and to scratch this off as a place for a beer.

I'll wait for the next iteration of a pub here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1yMOMB9dKgCe1JdsqPRs61B68LUjVME3NSmy2&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A great pub located in New Westminster. Fun place to watch sports on one of their many screens. Great happy hour selection on food and drinks. Spacious inside seating and patio seating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJKlxjM-cdlDjkSNjNjgqjYGqo7sQIEfH6hhg8&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Todd Hodgins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW72ymeCGuxhZLuxllkGl5JZOyyu8tehQoStTIzhCVPdDgNDg8L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Hidden gem for sure, but unlike some places that you secretly want to keep to yourself, this is one you want to tell friends about. Rarely do I give full ‚≠êÔ∏è across the board, but I honestly couldn‚Äôt find anything wrong that I would prefer differently.
May if there was more beer selection, but the offering are sufficient and satisfying. The food is good ‚Äúpub grub‚Äù with excellent flavors and choices.
Beef dip was superb, and the other sandwitch was a similar to a chicken parmesan with roasted veggies.
All good and definately worth the 15min wait. There‚Äôs very little sauce and the crust is bizarre. It‚Äôs almost like styrofoam - very airy without much substance to it and just kind of evaporates on your tongue.

The fusion slices were far superior to the classic slices. I found the tomato sauce much too sweet on the pepperoni or ham & pineapple. The slices with a garlic sauce base were much preferable.

[{"Name":"Keith Eastcott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk5BCUEJh42hOpsF-_OoCCbmyygcrHIJcijMiuq6slKML49qmN0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow. This is such a great restaurant. They were decorated for Christmas. Lots of decorations. They had a live band playing and a dancefloor if the mood strikes. The server was very friendly and accommodating. Food was incredible, I had chicken Cordon blue. I definitely recommend you try this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-KmHrZDFI0-VhBZOXUQSN_UP4HLecc9GU1jNN&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stephanos is a family favourite. We've celebrated many birthdays, and even hosted a 60th birthday party for 100 guests.

The Greek food at Stephanos is consistently delicious. I'd highly recommend the calamari. It's light, crisp and satisfying.

When ordering for a crowd, order a couple of platters and add extra dishes on. The Dinner Platters for 2 and Starter Platters are served with large portions. The dinner platters are served with rice, potatoes and 2 kinds of salad. We typically order Greek and Caesar salad.

Guests are served fresh, hot pita bread, covered in melted butter. We love it!

It's the perfect spot for a crowd. There's plenty of seating, it's easy to make a reservation, and the dining room is always decorated for the season.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY7XnxOWvyltveugWn5_48exh9Cg7MlFafTjkE&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We tried them and the service was excellent but the food was just OK. Most of us found it lacking flavour. We had beef souvlaki, chicken souvlaki which had no flavour, the roast lamb was good but nothing special, they had a lemon chicken rice soup that was decent and the Calamari was good. There was also an order of Teriyaki chick wings that were good. Nice wine selection and it was expensive for the quality of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKnRCX1s5zmqNVWx8ryzLuJieShk5jGydzePDC&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Cari del Caribe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm6firUBbVHSRlP2s4xiArkbddVcCCGxcWOmf78mRISiJv6uKo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great service..everyone was friendly and our server was lovely. Their group set menu was of so-so value. We didnt receive a fair amount of appies per person. The calamari, my favorite food, was bland. I enjoyed their lamb and potatoes, but found the rice and salad a bit bland. Atmosphere was great with a good live band with a small dance floor.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to come to order some Greek food! Absolutely no pride in what‚Äôs served, very disappointed, in my opinion, either change the process or shut this location down!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alli L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7M-K_wMLVOHyWDXpjXXk3pyMIn-Cv8yGLpMXYPKQoyxLDNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This service at this restaurant couldn‚Äôt get any more pathetic. I placed a very simple order on DoorDash with only 2 things. I got an order of onion rings, and the go-bucket, which includes a chicken slider & fries.

I received my delivery an hour later, and the only thing that was in the bag was 1 order of small fries. They forgot BOTH the chicken slider and my onion rings. Pretty unbelievable. Will never order from here again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Personal Coach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhqstV1InAkU4YOtXhoy5_IdbmLI1Ia3Xrxh6VaLMEccCUFBRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for Toonie Tuesday. EXCELLENT !! See pics. 1 large thigh, 1 plump drumstick, and 1 fries. Original recipe.
I took the picture after I ate half the fries. So I definitely recommend this location.
In Williams Lake I had a totally different / bad situation with Toonie Tuesday. So I really appreciate this KFC Location on 6th in New Westminster.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMS_g7r57gZ0JCBWaRBQMPqI5uyqNeHWs42gLmn&fid=0x0:0xdecded6c05c2ef19"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Peter Neuman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJH7-dyGV8WE5hQC6nbRvaAxggoN-aZdR3fZE-eEHybPwgwTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have frequented this KFC many times during COVID-19. Every one of my experiences, minus 1, has been great.

The one that wasn't so great was a mixup in my order request I made on the app for pickup. Specifically, the special instructions I added weren't followed, when on past orders they have been. I asked for mashed potatoes as my 2 large sides instead of the salads. For some reason their website, app and drive through menu don't list mashed potatoes as an option, even though they have them. Also, I upgraded my 2 fries to mega individual for an additional $1 total. I also asked for thigh only dark meat for the chicken. These 3 requests weren't met. I didn't check everything until I got home because the drive through was busy and it would have been a hassle opening all those containers in my car.

I provided feedback through the app. The next day I got a call from the store manager. She apologized and offered me 6 pieces of chicken, 2 large mashed potatoes and 1 large gravy as a resolution and acceptance of responsibility. I honestly wasn't expecting I would ever hear back at all. For this generous offer and the apology, which I accepted graciously, I give HUGE props to this store and manager for correcting and maintaining a positive customer relationship.

Then today I get a letter from KFC corporate apologizing and including a $10 coupon toward any purchase. Again, I didn't ask for our expect this! Well done again!

Also, at the drive through the workers wear masks, use hand sanitizer frequently and will substitute drinks for gravy without hassle of charge.

The food is enjoyable; the chicken tastes fresh, moist and has that yummy 11 herbs and spices goodness! It's why I keep coming back to KFC. I'll keep coming back to this KFC because of the impeccable customer service!

PS - there are really good coupons on their website that are customizable.

PSS - their strawberry cheesecake is awesome!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPbku4v19jb512LPUXFo9RnmlFgTZuC3vqAHHp&fid=0x0:0xdecded6c05c2ef19"],"When":"2020-9-10"},{"Name":"Steve Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIChg-sTXbvynXfOtQrXVIlLUNM015FBRILxInncYq16DD__w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Every time I order from here they gives you chicken soaking wet in grease. When I order from the other kfc on Kingsway there‚Äôs no issues. How hard is it to shake a basket and let the grease drain for 2 seconds? Instead there‚Äôs a puddle of grease at the bottom of a 6 piece bucket. Could only imagine what it would look like if I ordered more. Hopefully one day someone from kfc checks their restaurants and wonders what‚Äôs going on at this place. Complete circus, don‚Äôt order or eat here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Hanmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLW1n67jhxmYkpRJUpWO6KTn1Ti4ouX30asPEjYuCWdPuEEKsUJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Like every review on here it will be completely ignored by the franchise owner and store management. They dont care about us...anyways. Spare your health and don't waste your money.  $45 for a 10 piece bucket that came with 3 breast's and 7 drumsticks. What a joke, and to think we ordered here to give it another shot...lol Never again. Bye KFC üëã","Images":null,"When":""}]

Thank you very much, your service is the best","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNf4wDv2CawQUsVoirw-cM23_GLYmDEveeB3FyZ&fid=0x0:0x6832b1e7786a5ecc"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Edward Desaulniers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoP1wTU2-qZu4-kyQmMbasgYbLJv8tKfq6HxU12Zm-ypnqVMIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid fast food experience at this Burger King location. The Whopper was fresh and satisfying, and the fries were crispy. Service was quick and efficient, typical for a chain restaurant. While it doesn't offer gourmet dining, it delivers exactly what you'd expect from Burger King - reliable, familiar fast food at reasonable prices.

The restaurant was clean and well-maintained. During peak hours, there might be a short wait, but that's standard for popular fast food spots. It's worth remembering that as a chain restaurant, consistency is key, and this location meets that standard well.

If you're craving a quick burger fix in New West, this Burger King on 6th gets the job done without fuss. Just keep your expectations in line with what a fast food chain typically offers, and that you are paying under $15 per person, you'll likely leave satisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Bennett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgo_gtNIiDGiAGqUrnJ4WjhINfzlwjqXP70KnY7FOuJ0X5TAZq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The kitchen and till  should be more to the front for the public to see from the street .

[{"Name":"Ember Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMNJB74aKKAepkYhrktOEMZlPmYsfglhSTftpz8C9kzNV20Yo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The second we opened our pizza boxes, we knew this was the place for us. Absolutely AMAZING pizza, fresh dough,  tasty ingredients, and impeccable customer service. Highly recommend this pizza, and the location is the perfect distance from transit. Very informative and transparent about ingredients, and accommodation is available for vegans/dairy-free vegetarians.

If I could rate higher than 5 stars, I happily would. Give this place a try, you will certainly not be let down!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONDKMkR-k03sQFoj6VumJc_1lbnk7CZSIft3zi&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"K Volk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdqoSqm_pTdlU9e8Fq66CyWqpdPGbj2-ikus-uGI2GgFFLOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time ordering from this place, one of the very few places in new west with consistently high ratings on google.

Pizza came 20 minutes before their estimated time, and they include a real time tracking option with your email receipt allowing you to see exactly where your order is in the process of being made and delivered. The delivery driver was super friendly, all smiles, and courteous.

The pizzas are heavy weight for all the right reasons, hot, crispy on the outsides and not burned, with generous toppings from edge to edge. Did I mention they weigh a ton?

Highly recommend this place. Great pizzas for the price.

(Taco pizza / tropical Hawaiian with added chicken)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYxzTW97KDrmwWId3pa_EdznzVPU-FKihxTYeQ&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Madeline Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8xXkr3rdhtaU3CcLy3f0wDzhbxjacMKsMkIuTbIcC05n506g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was quite quick. Within 20 minutes of ordering at the till, order was ready. We got the Family Combo which was 1 large pizza (customizable toppings) a pasta and 2 cans of soda. Pepperoni pizza with extra cheese was great. Not too greasy & crispy pepperonis.

The lasagna was.. Not really a lasagna. The top cheese layer was great. But it seemed like the whole rest of the dish was lacking. It seemed like linguine with tomato sauce. No flat layers of lasgna pasta and no layers of ricotta cheese in between layers. Tasted fine but looked like an interpretation of lasagna for someone who hasn't had one before.

Would visit again but just for the pizza. Staff was friendly. Can't really say much for atmosphere since it was a quiet mid afternoon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuNN2vNmSalgI_ytLI1Jb30GUMhCDtF7BcloeQ&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Justin Turner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDNKnLtu91NUBVuNAL7AtG3Ix0GDRjtEMYDrnyWtG-OP4CFjOl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quality pizza. I got a meat lovers. I was seeing all the good reviews and had to come try it for myself.
If anyone has ever had Round Table pizza before, it is the cookie cutter pizza of that. Not that that is a bad thing! Very good cheese, decent ingredients and great crust.
Price is very good too. Would recommend in a pinch, can‚Äôt go wrong.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnss7wETzPYm0H8wwD7odAF6lvCWcO9JcYyfP1&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Margaret Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIN1PfctzO6HuL62iLRLZr8SliaKB1Hl5ynuYUIUqWdl_cBcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't had pizza this good in a while! Good amount of toppings right to the edge. Not too much so the crust nicely supports the toppings and does not soak through. Really good flavor. Ordered the chicken pesto, paneer, cheese, meat, and deluxe. All were great. Service was quick and timely even though they were busy. We will definitely be back. What a fantastic deal for their grand opening but their pizzas are absolutely worth full price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK5ssZB2bD2SnpfxUidGsG-ILQFiWzXYr_l6S9&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got a Hawaiian and a garlic chicken pizza. Love how the toppings are filled to the edge of the pizza, generous amount of cheese. The thickness is just perfect. I hope the restaurant can last at this difficult location. So happy to have a good pizza place close to home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_HRKj_19de50vsJDNRNW8LAh4JGUy5oodzF0W&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"K S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNs9D6cXyVPfmtabGvLUCC9wYXXIubSNTSPgQcaNUCxNDbHK9q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered 10 pizzas for a birthday party with an early pickup on a Sunday, and I can‚Äôt say enough about how fantastic our experience was! The staff were incredibly accommodating, ensuring everything was ready on time and exactly as we needed.

The pizzas were an absolute hit with all our guests! The butter chicken pizza stole the show‚Äîit was so popular that we ran out towards the end. Each pizza was perfectly cooked, generously topped, and packed with flavor.

If you‚Äôre looking for delicious pizza and exceptional service, this is the place to go. We‚Äôll definitely be ordering from here again for our next celebration! Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Henricksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkHUinAfyrJxB5VfntT8_gnt2PVnJS_entoTesQV1q8EAX0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Affordable and good quality pizza place.

I had a small deluxe. Lots of meats and cheese. I wish the beef was broken up.

Star deduction for the following:
Upon entry to pickup, there was a man behind the counter sitting and doing nothing. I said ‚Äúhello‚Äù and then ‚Äúhi‚Äù with no response. I assume it was the owner. I had to wait a short bit until staff from the kitchen who then came to the counter. I assume it was the owner. If you‚Äôre not going to even acknowledge customers entering, then don‚Äôt sit behind the counter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnn7Qa2nRyD4ir8fGJG0L_vJGMB7lpLs0haz_M&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-7-2"}]

[{"Name":"Maral H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv9KWxZkzAlGbT8_izCalAvL5ZD65gRqiUFXh0ROKqHLjdrt07=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not gonna lie . I was a little hesitant walking into Match (New West location) because it‚Äôs wasn‚Äôt busy but  I love how it was so  spacious ,I also noticed the different party rooms .
Glad I got to check it out tonight !
My Bartender ‚ÄúAlly‚Äù was very attentive and super friendly .  I trusted Ally with all the recommendations because Ally‚Äôs input was genuine and honest.  .

Had the Alfredo and shrimp dish and I wanted extra mushrooms and Ally was super accommodating and made it happen . Food was delicious and I got dessert to take home with me . I would definitely come back again. ‚Ä¶
ü§î Maybe even book a private party there in the near future !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOILSgSYR27Y7HUtI0rGuXDTKFvxY4WCYvVe0CB&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Lydia Nathe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN11wGOZlYbj2mxrkEpJC0C13ReaBejQPo_-hozaWwTeXumA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was terrible. The fact that there were so many different menus should have been the fist clue. I went for brunch and ordered a blackened shrimp benny. This consisted of 1 single tiny shrimp per Benny with the tiniest splash of hollandaise sauce, no flavor and dry. I couldn't even finish it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5Ofik1qCst-RcCDgqacobl-OdpLX4He1qrVJq&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Dan Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbNeFUlLkRmjcX25zxpAW7H_0IDjY0P_SfdPGvxnigSNv-OQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stopped in for dinner after an afternoon of shopping at Queensborough Landing and we were seated right away. Food is always reliable here and there are multiple sport screens for your entertainment. We ordered the Thanksgiving special turkey dinner and the 1/2 rack bbq ribs with chicken and subbed mashed potatoes for fries-both were delicious!
Service was efficient,food was hot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy_FTWHqZosJkliAtnezYOU6EW6icdWxym65ZV&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Jordana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJvxqFr8nGL8vok-SCRwxhp2_EJmOiFDFc3qAUH70xw1rrHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for a Saturday lunch with my family. It was fairly quiet which was nice. We were seated right away and the server was attentive. Ordered nachos and the beef dip
The nachos tasted great, not too salty and just the right amount of toppings. The chips were placed on a piece of tortilla so once yoyu've eaten all the chips, you could fold the tortilla and eat it with toppings that fell into it. Thought it was a great idea. The chips however were not crunchy. It was like stale chips that have been re-baked.
The beef dip was good. Good size and flavor. Ordered it with a side of ceasar salad thinking who messes up salads. Well, if you like eating whole cloves of baked garlic, then this is for you. I was not expecting to find a whole piece of garlic clove when I took a bite off my salad and it threw me off. Not sure if it was intentional but not a fan. Who wants to walk around the casino with garlic breath anyway.
Being it was a slow saturday afternoon - there were only about 5 tables around us-' we expected the washrooms to be clean. The ladies room was kept clean but hubby was disgusted with the mens room, described it as if it was not cleaned from the drinking that occured the night before. We had to tell the host about it and while he was quick to call someome to clean it, it should have been done without us having to ask them to do so.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZplm2z0ayKrtqPeLabwFidkci-dviicRQiEx7&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Lisa Avery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0uWvek94xw9hceZaor7-wGRHhxzIOVcSdxuCqWSKZC0HUDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly and efficient Gill was our amazing server and she was on top of everything. Super funny, very nice and fast-fast. Nashville Hot Chicken is my go-to here and it was as delicious as ever. The Tuna Bowl and the Heuvos Tacos were great. Thank you Gill!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPja0ZyExbuOpK6-_c4t4Ar2zI6M-Rrf0V76to&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place to have a nice dinner and drinks! The fried ravioli is a must-try! So delicious. I was so happy to see Goose Island IPA on tap here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKwXcakWHjZc55vrWM0xXJa9UZj-GGFoIyOPc6&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Harmeen Grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6oMbvuFAad35H3E9C4dkq0m-eZv18ucrsWsuAfPgn07nMwE8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible service! Asked the manager there who claims he‚Äôs the general manager for his name and he said he doesn‚Äôt need to share that. If you stand by your business, you shouldn‚Äôt need to hide your name. Very unprofessional. Just look at the picture of the water they service and instead of saying sorry about that and tries to explain the situation, he says I changed your water didn‚Äôt I? Very rude and unprofessional. Clearly too young to be able to handle the position he claims. The staffs are overworked and they need to do better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWh2R0zBT6XXtwHvK2q9AFBas0V51wghAawjKP&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Lilian Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeGvMKjLmGYYsJTNuBD99YNR1QBuoPNEayiKi_IYfH8GzSOqXQSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Match Eatery and Public House is an underrated treasure that has much more to offer than your average pub. Everything is always fresh, delicious, and thoughtfully prepared.

The happy hour deals are great, and the service is always friendly and attentive. They have private rooms that can be used for hosting events, making this place very suitable for gatherings or celebrations. If you are in search of a great atmosphere, excellent food, and versatility in the available spaces, this is the place!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Alli L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7M-K_wMLVOHyWDXpjXXk3pyMIn-Cv8yGLpMXYPKQoyxLDNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tried this place for the first time today and was beyond disappointed. The food was not at ALL as advertised. I ordered the Nashville hot chicken sandwich, which was advertised to come with crispy buttermilk fried chicken, pickles, onions, truffle aioli, and iceberg lettuce.

What I received was a wet, soggy chicken breast on a wet, soggy bun. There was coleslaw/carrots instead of lettuce, there were no pickles on my sandwich, which is one of the best parts of a chicken sandwich. There were a few tiny chunks of diced onion in the mix with the coleslaw. And there was no truffle mayo either. The fries were also somehow completely wet and soggy.

I paid over $25.00 for slop and unfortunately did not get refunded. I do not recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFa-AiBhNRJPZ_aWRdJc_bTImbiCeEALqEdEkB&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Theresa Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLecCztY_pXmy93BikSwe6M0XhZAjBKcATWBvCksY1zqc7aJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently went here with friends while we were in town for the Grey Cup.  The happy hour prices were pretty great,  the food was delicious, but the service was the best part! Our server Tracy was exceptional! She was friendly,  helpful, and treated us very well! We will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLs6IW7OkXDNG_1x32NBJKHG0qD7nn4sWezhaZnNXJFbWqGcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Last night, we reserved a table for 16 people (family and friends for the family wedding this weekend). We were outside on the patio that was set up for us when we arrived.  Everything about the service and food and atmosphere was excellent.  Tracy and her colleagues were attentive and treated our bride and groom so well!
The wood fired pizzas were cooked to perfection, the beer was flowing and the cocktails were so yum.  This place was a great hit with our UK and Australian folks.
Tracy, your service, attention to detail and cheery smile was the highlight of our evening! You must have been so tired after the young ones left! Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Hatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUe7DIzvoENQZ4GjCw_X6rw3ru2I8LVPZqfs82HioYw6dYMZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! We were just in New Westminster for a night and needed a place for dinner. So glad we stumbled upon Howe Sound Taphouse. The smash burgers with bacon are the perfect size, and you can sub out the fries for an array of other options, like a caesar salad, soup, or poutine. Tracy was our server and she was top notch. Her recommendations were spot on and even gave us ideas of things to do on our road trip through western Canada. Give this place a try if you‚Äôre in the area. They will not disappoint! Oh and try the stickey toffee pudding with ice cream. So good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUha4uw8a4ALc1AAbzAulLyf7pPcko2YbFZc2Q&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Katherine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqeXJrpSHxfX8GE1npRfPdH-neJmrhomz_5TbH53kcZeP_LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an awesome visit. The wings were fresh and delicious, it was a nice welcoming atmosphere but Tracy as our server was tremendous. So attentive, and so engaging.  I cross my fingers I get her as a bartender/server next time I come in!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Golden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6-VcfVSb5XiaNXuNybTZd8dFS8O8_6G4ifg6tWxwz1edWTIVr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a great experience at this location. Our server was absolutely amazing and I wish I could find my receipt that showed her name. She was very informative on all of our food and drink selections.
We had the pizza selection, the table was full of pizza and it was the best choice. Wildfire and great crust with a good amount of toppings. You could easily share the pizza with a friend or eat it yourself. We did decide to have dessert as it was house made and not brought in by bulk.  Cheese cake, wow! Simply devine. I'm allergic to the topping it came with and the chef was kind enough to make me a topping I could eat, that's above and beyond service. I highly recommend the pizza and cheese cake.
Great selection of beer, there is something for all tastes. Pop and cocktails available along with mocktails.
It has a really comfortable atmosphere but very Bar like. there is a patio but we arrived in a rain filled night so had to sit inside. It's clean and inviting.
Great location in new Westminster, if you're taking the SkyTrain it's right next to a station, Columbia I believe. If you're driving there is some parking out front. If not there is public pay parking a few blocks away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had to see the New Howe Sound Brewing location in New Westminster. I enjoyed happy hour beer. It is still a comfortable community sports pub at its heart. The happy hour selection and food choices are good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5NXiS0BComNbFvti0ln9vMik4SamoRgUCGgpy&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-1-27"},{"Name":"Laura Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvFXX3bki0RGZbBISaWYaQdevOgHG4YwN6p2rh1Dtj-SGMLXEz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A week ago I was part of a group of 30 and we had a great time partying in the back patio area.  The weather cooperated and the staff reserved the upper patio area for us.  We had a smaller menu to choose from but there was still a lot of choice.  I enjoyed the Smash Burger and everyone seemed to enjoy their food as well.  Good beer and reasonable prices.  No complaints from anyone.  We had excellent service as well.  The pub has a compfortable atmosphere.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Lucy Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuwCjTEBDQem6hcfmmxSA0I0nNlJPkS88N0KyjwlMUZAjI_Jdm8w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So so good! We went on a Saturday afternoon (around 1pm) and the wait was ~30 mins. I ordered the half sweet & half savoury brunch meal with the sweet berries, french toasts, scrambled eggs and sausage and it was so yummy. Their portions are so filling and everything I ordered was really good. Their fruits are also really fresh and the sweet strawberry jam sauce is so delicious. Their pannekoek (pancake) is my favourite so I recommend! The service was also amazing despite the store being so busy. Will definitely come back to try other stuff on their menu as they offer a huge variety of brunch items :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxixr8Uc4FBVc7gNi14uuf6Qs4kxmbSuJz-OxI&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Sky Eyes Video","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2JXXl5yK-thMqk8EUNl3FWmyw5SFqlc_KvzAMt-0MdDn-UuKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far, the best breakfast place we have tried in the Lower Mainland. The food is always delicious, the service is quick and kind and the management is excellent. We never hestitate to recommend this restaurant to anyone visiting the GVRD. Located at the New Westminster Quay, you get to enjoy a wonderful breakfast, brunch or lunch with an historic view of the Fraser River.

We were so happy to share the Big Pannekoeken Breakfast (it was enormous!) and to enjoy their delicious Lattes. Do not miss out on their Fruit Cups/Bowls. They're the best in town. Not sure how, but they always find the best, freshest fruit around for their fruit bowls! Really can't say enough good things about this gem of New Westminster.

Be sure to check them out whether you're a New West Local or just visiting for the day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONWM7nSkoypP2p-LJnDbDE_pLEsSck0rRO_Ic2&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Ashley Beck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2go2YhxSI7EswM_VSBvu_ZrkSgFk9Mlc_bhBuN0qSdy7S-csG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so glad I found this place, it‚Äôs so refreshing to have a young staff and all of them are so incredibly on point, polite, friendly, all around gave fantastic service every visit I‚Äôve had. I worked in hospitality for years, am a foodie and they do it RIGHT. I cant say enough good things. The fruit bowl is out of this world! I haven‚Äôt had such a great bowl at a restaurant in Canada. It‚Äôs like being in Sydney - the kitchen was fully capable of serving my request of ‚ÄúNO melon‚Äù and has never had an issue doing so... Highly recommended! I would give 10 stars if I could.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0tVduAYNmIQ5WBiMBLJZo8SXTuJjOjV7-nxYx&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Wong Mirkit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjiJ8ex8j1X0oWn9473ThU96BZenBcIeH5TCzgYCkF3KSF10c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It‚Äôs a fantastic meal with nice view here. I am very impressed with the fruit dish which contains over 15 species of fruits and all is so fresh and tasty. The medium egg Benedict is awesome too. The service is perfect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDBEIXQHDxodc_nbrABn3XE77R62wwOOgPNf8P&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Kristy Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEfZ2rjxNiODjhooQ3vu4wU52UFmMssx1nBEw-QrGtiP3D8nPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simple brunch food, but things are cooked well. No complaints, but also nothing super special. Open to coming again for classic brunch food. Their side of fruits are great, quality and quantity wise.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcLAD95E-5bsvErMqbBg_EelX3vRtaVcz0QVp_&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Melanie E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR0bJcxqNkJt-i1wxCH3EaQXevncA86panZszfT__NAs_0KWRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My friends and I came here for brunch on the weekend. We all enjoyed our meals.

Atmosphere: 5/5 - if it's a beautiful day, go for the outdoor seating near the water. There's also interior seating too with a nice vibe to the place

Food: 4/5 - Two of us had the breakfast platter of chorizo sausage with fresh fruit, roasted potatoes, toast and choice of 2 eggs and the other ordered the savory Dutch Pannekoeken with two range eggs, and turkey bacon. All servings were of decent portions. There are choices for the gluten-free and the vegetarians. A great place for breakfast.

Server - 4/5 - friendly and helpful. It took a bit of time to get our meal.

Parking - 3/5 - metered parking nearby with insufficient parking spots.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMppjHBLiiYCVf10A0RMOBucmxc7_CYPhu4UFRm&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Virginia Barazzuol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLL7wkWLIn3uxnKGJhdMyd6yiile32ZYmw8MVcgdfWI-jdUHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The whole experience was wonderful, good food beautiful view, nice atmosphere ... BUT The fruit bowl at this restaurant tis the most amazing fresh and exotic fruit you will see! Also if you're hot sauce lover you can get a see election of 8 different hot sauces to choose from... Amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6apN0qvMNFOUnWYWwmXnBCk1BMG6gYT1Do_o2&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHTcuSM-4ly1uIP3q2-jgQ_2Vqi7GhBmGO9JykCcOlnN1NYOmqYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I know it‚Äôs a sin to order lunch/dinner at a breakfast place, but I‚Äôm not huge into brekkie. I took a risk and got the fried fish sandwich with salmon and it was amazing! Super fresh fish, not heavy on the breading, and the coleslaw on the sandwich is a great ‚Äúsauce‚Äù addition. Would def go again despite not being a breakfast person!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSbgvCceux2QU4ioSPfC8pkT4H16Oyy_5ot_jv&fid=0x0:0xc258dc25b32ed8e4"],"When":"2024-8-25"}]

[{"Name":"Joe W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWr5W9mdlAV3O23BOO4Bd8Ea19vBOm9lh8GncQo9V3SBCJlUG7Jow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Do not come here unless you have plenty of time to spare.  The food was decent but you can hardly find anyone when you need them.  There were only 3 tables on the dining side but at least 3 occasions we had to walk into the back area to find a staff ourselves.  There was simply nobody around out there.  They are either seriously understaffed or the staff just weren't paying attention to the customers' need.  Either way, management needs to work on their service level.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Hill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV5D3pd1-7f1WRg6mfB7OdEUHbR8vKhmA1KworYfcg3p7kPpUu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"To be clear, this was the very first time I have been back at Boston Pizza in over a year as their prices keep going up and the food hasn‚Äôt certainly gotten any better.  The service last few times wasn‚Äôt great either.

So I waited a while to order. I ordered a margarita and some prawn fettuccine and waited and waited and waited. Finally, the majority came to the table and told me that as their blender was broken I should order something else to drink so I asked for a margarita on the rocks

After waiting a long time again, I was told by the same individual that they couldn‚Äôt make that either and I should ask for something else again
I asked for them to surprise me with something lime flavored

Eventually, my waitress showed up and apologized and told me that the blender wasn‚Äôt working. I told her that I had asked the bartender to surprise me, but since that wasn‚Äôt coming anytime soon, it seemed I just wanted to cancel it.

Shortly after this, she brought me food. After a few bites I realized my spicy prawn fettuccine had no prawns and was not spicy either. She had brought me the wrong food.

This officially confirmed that I will not be coming back to Boston Pizza probably at any location due to their overly high prices for Italian food, which is some of the cheapest food to make on the planet","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erica EDMAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtbgYq8CYPacpxIsi-vVF8k4WDkLqimMZbC08jZPNycTuc4Mo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boston Pizza, as a corporate brand, is not only a place where we can enjoy delicious meals but also a venue that supports sports and has a global reach. It‚Äôs a comfortable space to relax, eat, and have fun, thanks to its excellent employees and the amazing flavors they serve. When you combine all of this, everything comes together perfectly. That‚Äôs why I highly recommend it‚Äîyou should definitely try it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"E A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2tr69zditFgb4vd9PKKPg-4vyS0N5C24WXnk5zPZlDs-IhA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All our food was delicious, portions are huge, restaurant and bathrooms are very clean, and our server Parul was very sweet and kind, attentive, always smiling, and didn‚Äôt forget anything we asked for. We had an international guest with us and she loved it, great experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ1OrgD7yv88cJlOFM0_lUDSi5otOBXam9J_vZ&fid=0x0:0xf56f0ca3eefb9c0"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Jack SUNSET","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4IWe2Is123c_lBB-O0he2VLMZyE3yBWLFtFUOkDMxLedOdeU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"‚ÄúThis is a perfect place to go with your family for a meal. The atmosphere is very romantic in the evenings, and you have the chance to watch your favorite sports on big-screen TVs. The staff is incredibly polite, and the food is delicious. I highly recommend it, and I insist you give it a try. Thank you!‚Äù","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clement Tsang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlnMDAP3bpkDDKvV1biwN8gKMqY9QPN2tRRszD8X2osjIyB-xd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unbelievable.... absolutely horrendous. My most worst dining out experience in all my decades.

Arrive here at 5:53pm with my pregnant wife for Valentines day dinner because she wanted the heart shaped pizza. Ordered by 6:05 and left us with waters, this would be the last time our server came to our table. 3 tables near us as we witnessed sat down after us, ordered and got their food. Around 6:45 I walked up to the heat lamps and asked for service and demanded we get service. They came with the food we ordered! Yay? Nay.... it was cold and dried. Absolute garbage but still no server to be seen. I grabbed all my plates of food and brought it back to the heat lamps and told them it's all dried and cold.

Around 7pm somebody, I believe was a line cook or dishwasher, helped bring some food out. 1 out of 3 items served. We started eating it. At this point I realized under one of the pizzas was something that looks like a mostly eaten garlic bread!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Disgusting.

A food runner came by with our 2 other plates while the table next to us finished their meal and I told her about it. She said she will bring it to her manager and did not come back since.

While eating the other 2 plates we noticed smaller things we could live without complaining to them. Bunched up calamari, unmixed and smaller portion of the Jambalaya, a random pasta that looked like a kids pasta in the Jambalaya.

Still no sign of the server. Another food runner came by at the end and said our meal was taken care of and apologized for everything.

I used to frequent another Boston Pizza location that was closed down. I'm not coming back ever.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3otXGw4aI1aOeypbrytEoOSDZFwT1Ov-kfcOq&fid=0x0:0xf56f0ca3eefb9c0"],"When":"2023-2-15"},{"Name":"James Coles-Nash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkJrmtjWT371XtK4SkdD-gc4742YrtKT1KSibl27VRSYpTt9Yi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Sooo bloody slooooow, took 10 minutes to get seated in an empty restaurant, 30 to get our order in, 30 to wait for food, and another 15 to get our bloody bill! Did I mention they were empty? Two waitresses running around like headless chickens. The food was pretty obviously prepared in a warehouse somewhere frozen and then re heated, I swear the chicken soup was canned Campbell's reheated multiple times. I will never come back to this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXA_fURXHer7FBkbuFw6LvlQ2wgnQGKmqY7Wlq&fid=0x0:0xf56f0ca3eefb9c0"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Amy Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1Fqng1TSwXq9T24MRYmHHHX9f4qHb56PSWtHso-CGga0uBLtUFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Generally good, quieter dining experience. Normally great service, but would not honour sign found on Westminster highway advertising 10% off on pick-up orders. Was told that nothing was known about it. Would recommend that the sign is removed to avoid confusion","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmY_StewA_w-zvuy80_gS44FJRj6e1eMVDwjpS&fid=0x0:0xf56f0ca3eefb9c0"],"When":"2024-6-1"}]

[{"Name":"Evelyn Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXInuLivNU3_4_Fb29KcZR5WILPoO9N4aWVZYBZmlRc5aJadHZq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visited, I was impressed by the services and food. The grilled squid is really nice, I don‚Äôt see this dish in every restaurant. Clam pasta and crab cake are standard. 10 oz Steak is very nice for the price, cannot request more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUQ7nsyBFqrtXgNv0HzZXulfLvBnQI2fOqyzDG&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Karlee P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKcogQ6RORYiMmSspqCcqCmyIrc0-pWDzMzKeIGrxpNySqDxSl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Piva is perfection, all day long. Their brunch menu has so many options, and we were so thrilled with everything we ordered. The restaurant is cozy and elegant, and made for a great girls‚Äô day out brunch. Don‚Äôt forget to make a reso! Thank you for having us!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDay9lWCZKCw8GroovHQUVnnpWdYSpXdFtDu38&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We just celebrated our anniversary at Piva several this week. We shared dishes including carpiacco, wild boar meatballs, duck & fig pizza, stewed beef rib, and tiramisu sundae. The food is okay, the service is excellent. I like that they gave us a complimentary brownie for our celebration. The wild boar meatballs were my favorite that night, 10 out of 10, juicy & savoury. The stewed beef rib was average, it was tender but the flavor was not special, I'd love if it's served with mashed potatoes instead of polenta.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaUmkMqgu8vd6nr2sYsNCMhb8A4iYXQtDujjQw&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Mel Watson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5VTs1jV9mGHt6OL9qkfUDCZGdH17wqi7trSn7ITXDNc6XzIfQGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My boyfriend took me here for my birthday dinner, and I was honestly amazed the whole time!
The service is absolutely stunning. Our waiter (I believe his name was Darryl but I could be wrong) was so hospitable, kind, and a funny gentleman!
The drinks are SO original and just delicious! I highly recommend the Viola drink. It was so good that when my boyfriend stole a sip of mine...he ordered one for himself!
The food was great. We had the warm olives and the Brussel sprouts to start, the miso carbonara and modern Italian pizza for mains, and the restaurant surprised me with a beautiful birthday dessert!
We will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHQx58gP0fXtUAbWAKE7HFST9iFOwmjJ2MM8ZL&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Manmeet Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMXWGi0PTwBnnJPx-2zRWWQX9viRcadnjBye5zp3cT1qRomGuzzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good customer service, server was nice and polite. She was checking in before, during and post meal. The food options were less as it was brunch menu at 1330 for some reason. I wish there were more options as only three pasta choices were available. For an italian restaurant, we expected a few more dishes in pasta style. The food tasted good. The flavours were good and rich. The service was pretty well timed, with no excessive wait time. The atmosphere was good at the restaurant as well, not too loud, not too quiet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPU26a65QhL0Sk96k43AZHN5yARJkPc7IPH4QF0&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Jamie Coo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMtT8SYH3ODglSdZyhsIz5N_cesns6jNpwE2VJCXq0WPBgF9EA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Highly recommend having a reservation before coming, the place filled up really quickly eventhough we came here for a dinner on a weekday. Service in general was pretty good, most food items were also good. We had the brussel sprouts and fritters to start - brussel sprouts were super crispy and flavourful, while the fritter is also pretty good but nothing too special. For main we ordered the Chef's Best pizza, Duck & Fig pizza, Duck, Halibut, and the Sable Fish to split among the table. Highly recommend the Chef's Best pizza and the Halibut - they were definitely our favourites. Duck was also really enjoyable - the cherry reduction went super well with the meat, but it is a bit pricey as the dish only came with 2 pieces of duck. We were quite disappointed at the Duck & Fig pizza as everything was too dry, feels like there is not enough sauce/fig jam. The Halibut itself was cooked to perfection with amazing texture, but the sauce is waaay too salty. For dessert we ordered the lemon tart and the affogato. The lemon tart was great - perfect balance of sweetness and tartness, and the berry jam on the side went really well with the tart. The affogato was just average.
Overall we had a great experience here, and we are quite interested to try their brunch menu as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvR0ogf3PJ6ES4lIO6J1FXeYlBD4j5CK0wpcpV&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Kristy Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEfZ2rjxNiODjhooQ3vu4wU52UFmMssx1nBEw-QrGtiP3D8nPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Yummy Italian food, it is on the pricier side. The lamb chops are great. The pasta is amazing half the time, hit or miss depending on the day. I‚Äôve had it when the pasta was super soggy and also had al Dante before. I wouldn‚Äôt mind coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvTHVqm5F8jYm47yg6tSVndEM40mSAdxk1UGOM&fid=0x0:0xefee1f34aa4d5625"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Joanna Fahmy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTznlA_q5Xa6Whv5wHF-yEDXEyOSOXOXBiPU7xtZRDBuF4Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Came here for a birthday dinner with my in laws, the food was okay, not as good as I thought it would be. The portions weren‚Äôt bad for mains but the appetizers were quite small.
