user_reviews:
[{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you like the vintage ambience, you will not disappointed.   All the decorations, the train, lighting, antique tables and chairs are so attractive.
The food are much better than what we expected.  All the meals are all inclusive.
One dish includes a warm medium bread with garlic butter, soup or salad, tea or coffee and ice-cream in one very reasonable price.
The prices are really reasonable for the food quality.  The streamed one pound mussel is only $10.95 and the quality and portion are good.  All the food come out fresh and hot.
Our server is friendly and helpful.
They also offer happy hour.  The prices are more reasonable too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrI1NaEKk18zPVLWjXeCK07YJnH9IyejK96tzI&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX11ANDfpnFU7GmCeaVtU5cBwuWRqquWAK3F9_AUyciKpah0H5L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High on a hill in New West is a very prominent beige, brick and green building, home to The Old Spaghetti Factory, a family friendly restaurant famous for their "it's all included" slogan.

I've been eating here for years and the food has remained relatively the same throughout. Pasta is their mainstay and they have heaps of it paired with a litany of sauces. Appetizers aplenty and drinks galore round out a very robust menu so there is no way that you will leave hungry.

As if that wasn't enough incentive to visit, I can vouch for the astounding efficiency of the servers. Literally just as soon as you place your order, that's how fast your meal is delivered. A quick succession of drinks, followed by your soup or salad and then very shortly afterwards, your main meal.

And of course, the most important thing: The food is filling and delicious, and the prices are by far some of the cheapest around.

In an age where price gouging has become the norm, it is so refreshing to see that some places aren't out for your money, and instead are more concerned with customer satisfaction. I assure you, the experience at Old Spaghetti Factory will never get "old".","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8K66T6181PkX__5WP8s9IAXwgtF6s9kgrOVJi&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"sara karimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1XYkwzloxYSsc1EqxvBP-2Mv59HBF7-8-P7UFahyIx3LfqNI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"‚ÄèOld Spaghetti Factory is one of the best restaurants in great Vancouver.
‚ÄèThe atmosphere is fabulous, you will enjoy all of antique tables and chairs, decorations and the lovely train in the middle of restaurant. When you are walking around, old pictures catch your eyes. All of these brings smile to your mouth and good feeling and happiness to you.
‚ÄèThe start with bringing fresh bread with garlic butter that is so tasty and if you want more, they bring you. Also, salad or soup at the beginning and coffee, tea or ice cream at the end is included in your food. Food is delicious. We got Fettuccine Alfredo with chicken and lasagna. They were delicious, however the portion of lasagna is so small, I wish it was bigger than that.
‚ÄèAlso, drink we got was good as well.
‚ÄèPrice is reasonable.
‚ÄèThe only complaint is although there were a lot of free tables on the floor and trains, they gave us a table in mezzanine and when we asked to have a table in the train they said you have to wait for 20 minutes! And also other parts of the restaurant is closed!
‚ÄèAnyway, I highly recommend Old Spaghetti Factory. You will enjoy the time and food a lot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeks5UyNYwMesTqd1OPMBx-5OYcdJnlY2ekXzD&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The Old Spaghetti Factory consistently delivers, and their new West location is no exception. We adored the warm atmosphere and were impressed by the excellent value offered by their All-Inclusive meal options. However, the real steals were the succulent mussels for under $11 and the half-liter of house wine for under $14 ‚Äì the perfect finishing touches to an already outstanding dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5QzZrrk03TLI0HLb9z2GGf5jqWAJ6evFql9s7&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Yvonne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj_HNmRFhr0uY3k5KAoKohOmCo83kG-cmVR_BGACYiBkVXvGMN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down our favorite place to eat out when we want a great meal. I have been to other locations but this is definitely my first choice. Great food at a reasonable price. They always treat us well and reserving a table is easy to do.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_RCcKQ-tgRt6Qu2y5p_ZuX6tR2KCRMIFfX8YZ&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Chinmayi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH4UnNpio-g5tml4wocrS6R0rqjdOLc0uP2LiNmjrAs61LNoo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the food and atmosphere. Food tastes very good and authentic, I love how they serve soup or salad with mains and you get an ice cream at the end. The bread and butter at start tastes very good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2TTjezrL4hulDStRQxIGgpd23SiqbWaUM1vDu&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"carly simon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQF_aGyoPI8H3LYAhNV4wwR-mqrrjL3yRed1ybzkG5ohunzlM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Old Spaghetti Factory in New Westminster has been an integral part of our family‚Äôs journey for over 45 years, serving as the backdrop for countless celebrations. So, when my grandmother was asked where she wanted to mark her 101st birthday, there was no hesitation‚Äîshe chose the New West Old Spaghetti Factory.

Owner Clinton and his incredible team went above and beyond to make this milestone truly unforgettable. From the warm welcome to the thoughtful touches throughout the evening, every detail was perfect. The food, as always, was delicious‚Äîcomforting, consistent, and just as we remembered from so many special occasions.

What stood out most was the genuine care and attentiveness of Clinton and the staff. They made my grandmother feel celebrated and cherished, which means more to us than words can express.

Thank you, Clinton, and the entire team for creating yet another beautiful memory for our family. We look forward to many more celebrations with you in the years to come.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRkruIYyYsm5LJ6KOxmILJLCHcRtSKtb0rVedB&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Leon Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPOnBvlGz2k_WzxOhCiURR3aRaAE5ffHXfUBJJ4GP7GBC5Wn8K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Your typical Old Spaghetti Factory here, and it‚Äôs quite delicious! They have some nice portion sizes, especially since a soup and bread is included with their pastas. We also got their peach Bellini, which was very well made. I highly recommend 	their shrimps also :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsk5sX7bOYqULK1asqrgtdNWH3FvNHXR7vnOaA&fid=0x0:0xe216b5a28ce125ce"],"When":"2024-9-21"}]

[{"Name":"Afa Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhTgagBDdHz09XPRGJJA4c38TAv-F1f6HV90y0-8_ALLfJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a lovely little hidden gem in Victoria Hill! We went on a Friday and sat on the patio, which had nice big umbrellas for shade. Started with the White Blossom and Fennel Salad. Both very good and very well portioned!! The pizzas to follow were also very good. The ambience and attention to detail on both the food and decor makes this place exceptional. Can‚Äôt wait to go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5dPHNdYNHumoL0hIbzcJfr0IYyxZkaV8mvW8&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Beste Beksac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRHrZjQZ2Y7U8imEaoQIIwf8XpiwCv-hJrFmMIImXOYQ0KsPM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved everything we tried!
The Rocketman pizza had amazing ingredients and a perfect crust. The Lambada pide was super tasty, and the Tiramisu was perfectly balanced. We enjoyed every bite! We‚Äôll be back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN34zPfPzgqIxZM4aEbND6Fy2SNohDflUN9mkM&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Thomas Cybucki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7aEXuW8hZrTVGQNEHTg42jfPaI_0ku-Xj046mhe9grmyBSnST=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying L'Onore, and it's one I've been wanting to try for a while. Didn't have a reservation so we were seated at the bar, which was just as good for the two of us.

My wife really enjoyed her Old Fashioned drink, I just had a beer on tap. We ordered the warm olives to start then shared two pizzas. The dough was fresh and had a nice, light crispiness just on the outside. Sometimes I find when we get this style of pizza from places, the toppings will be sparse. But we didn't feel that here, there was a good amount and definitely didn't feel like we were eating dough and tomato sauce. Loved the two we got (one was the Diavola),  and we definitely want to come back and try some other ones on the menu. Really enjoyed our dinner!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjBOfU_qNJ0Ks20bzlNO8bsBz7BxK8qQ8LJlvz&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Stephanie Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPpmqBG5uFjOO9zH3oPC1YLF3gyloafpU1sWsK191vkcK-dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There's pizza, and then there's PIZZA. This pizza is definitely quality over quantity. We got the Funguy and the Diavolo. The Diavolo was a masterpiece, a new combination of flavours that I had never tried before and we loved it. It was savoury, sweet and spicy.  The prices were very reasonable, and the two of us left feeling full and satisfied, but not bloated and regretful. The dining ambiance was really nice. I don't remember seeing a tv in there, and there was no super loud music either, which I liked a lot. It was relaxing and not overstimulating. Everyone working was friendly and took the time to acknowledge our presence. We will definitely be back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLhQJIWm1Mv9Qh1EaFViiHHpnj59FEEs3xb3N1&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"C B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU5ZahqHZDQJLqv2VLadq649JlqVkofuVk4HKRBFcswCnTXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This used to be my go to...but when my pizza arrives super soggy, not even cut...I will never order take out again. Eating in service is great, and when I called to let the manager know about items in my pizza that did not belong...he was great. Hopefully you can get back to what you were like when you first opened","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxkggX2rk7x4xtwlrT7aa14dJEMC75XFFzwU96&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Grace Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv2Qb5BK8BlHD8B-fNqpMIiwBP96of3n6s7qsHpu4xPXVSJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A friend suggested this place for a ladies night! Soooo good! Made fresh, very unique pizza names such as ‚Äúunicorn‚Äù pizza with corn!! They have gluten free options too! The staff were very nice and the drinks were great too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQe0kI1Cj515tDGAurKUfc2R4kmW8Z0NWowYPf&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Larissa De Melo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXS7LlTvOBr91XzsML1fqci8yQw0llVT4I5YtVz_NTJfdC_iYlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good pizza, one of the best I've ever had in metro Vancouver. Tasty, fresh, good ingredients. The staff was friendly. Quite small space, but worth waiting a bit. Street parking is hard to find, but they have underground parking, entrance in the back (signage could be better for that).
Just wish the pizza was a bit cheaper so I could go back more often!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfdL-j3-NSSXhTGTO_2dObL2zA-DIFmBDo3mXt&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Epitome of quality over portion size. This is one of my partner‚Äôs favorite pizza places. Atmosphere is cozy and our server was excellent. I personally liked NYCHEESE over ROCKETMAN. It is a very good pizza indeed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzyIRZJTLUQhDH2JmuP3CfoJ7_fJsT9RDJcFec&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-3-9"}]

This is my favourite place to go for good comfort food. Everything just tastes homemade (in a good way) and made fresh. All day breakfast, decent prices, cozy old school diner type atmosphere‚Ä¶ everything about this place is just comfortable and calm. I love it. For breakfast I love their crab cake benny, for lunch their beef dip or clubhouse is amazing ‚Ä¶ honestly though I don‚Äôt think anything would disappoint on their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOn5pc2QqA1lNmg4R5xvn-6iOJ-4hDoQthO7_cS&fid=0x0:0x77295d980dad15d0"],"When":"2023-5-24"},{"Name":"Tina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAKiC5J1ql1LsLTTfBwgvAj6sVGUusHXghumDKVG9ZTQ8QjcD_1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"SO GOOD! ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•

If you‚Äôre looking for a cozy, no-frills, bang-for-your-buck brunch place, this is IT.

We got here at around noon on Sunday, they‚Äôre busy, with a queue outside. We waited around 15 min for a table for 2.

Really friendly service right off the bat. We got our coffee with a handful of creamer. Our food came QUICK! And it tasted as delicious as it looked. We got 2 coffees, a grill lite, a sixth street hash, and a side of bacon; came to around $43 after tax

Kathy, our server, was so friendly and attentive. Thank you Kathy for making our experience so wonderful!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl6Sb_FcbYYSvKTTdWzgWgBnGkoUOXepx9BCQi&fid=0x0:0x77295d980dad15d0"],"When":"2023-11-28"},{"Name":"Gulnur Sultanova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuYGDYaVeVLlUwM-htQX7w_i6mT3hy5fnLa6BTq7BlM9oujRE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place, quality food, friendly staff. My appreciation to the chef for very tasty and delicious dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8lj6xFQc1C-pxFS7iq-n4tva632MvsR5XKAJu&fid=0x0:0x77295d980dad15d0"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"BON Barker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6s4O1HFf2haa-W9xjuPJPsbT_ooYYBv4BFI-p1az4VXJBlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great old school diner. Simple food that is done right. Friendly efficient staff. Prices are extremely reasonable, especially considering you are in Vancouver. I personally love locations that are true original 70's diners that are what they are with little change. I would definitely recommend stopping by. We ate here twice. The first time, there was ample seating, and the second time, we waited for a while to get a seat. Both times, the food came out quickly with the same quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPR1UgOV10rQHiPAJ5AkS1EaMSuRkd2vJo69fBy&fid=0x0:0x77295d980dad15d0"],"When":"2023-6-18"},{"Name":"Adam Hatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUe7DIzvoENQZ4GjCw_X6rw3ru2I8LVPZqfs82HioYw6dYMZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great little greasy spoon in New Westminster. The breakfast hits the spot. I got the eggs, bacon, potatoes and white toast. If you‚Äôre feeling a lighter breakfast, you can get the single waffle and add a side. Real maple syrup is also available upon request. Friendly staff and warm atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDB4eS-AVejb2STpNVk9u-U3BuzaAybtJAVdI-&fid=0x0:0x77295d980dad15d0"],"When":"2024-5-8"}]

[{"Name":"Andrew Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK13LuhtbcQQQ1wDmBa9J0Vwn9ABCTfxSFuyxqkVS3IT67IVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amelia restaurant on 12th Street in New Westminster offers an exceptional breakfast experience that combines great value with friendly service. The menu features a variety of hearty options, from fluffy pancakes to savory omelets, all made with fresh ingredients that elevate the meal. The portions are generous, ensuring that diners leave satisfied without breaking the bank. The staff is attentive and welcoming, creating a warm atmosphere that makes you feel right at home. Whether you're a local or just passing through, Amelia is a must-visit for anyone seeking a delightful start to their day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNKEjRXEuOKsGVqiSXdN-aPrRaezPFRonRpRrC&fid=0x0:0x96f31292f36a860a"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Honest Reviews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8H803fKx1YqmW2UYOqm_SSmbFPJq9HKHS8Q8uYcbaiump3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here with a friend for breakfast and the food was good.  Portion size was okay and the price was reasonable.

Service was very good as the staff refilled my grinds coffee 3 times!!!

Other breakfast places slowly increase their price and decrease their portion size and forget what their business is suppose to be (example Jimmy‚Äùs Place Restaurant on North Road Coquitlam)

Will come back again 100%","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C P√©rez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWILDNLHQbwQ4WYh0f_XaV2u7QTtA8bZ0QNemPRYV6F4iiNEtYnbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We visited this local restaurant this morning for the very first time. [{"Name":"Alina Emery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFFXXc2y2gjjUEfjvZr7gv44kQb-MPmzWUcV4nZl5nDLrvQSAXAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Split the sushi boat with some sake and it was really delicious! We had to stop and grab something to eat quickly as we had a 5month old needing to eat too. The servers were super lovely and food came to us very quickly! Felt very homey and food was great. Only feedback is having a space to change diapers would be a 10/10 but loved everything else! Will be back soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Makoto Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTTV198NAfai_RKRHly1LIX-gqZYSb8Sv-UnCFgLBSyAxhsz0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ikoi Sushi used to be our favorite sushi place, but unfortunately today is our last day here.

There is a new policy that is $15 minimum order per person. We completely get it.
After ordering food, we let the server knows we will order more later. But when the other server (older lady) brought us food she told us to pay for the complementary tea.
The way she told us was rude and unprofessional.
(She said "You only spent $12" "You have to pay for the tea!")

Also, we felt the food portion became smaller than before.

I'm not going to write everything down here but after all the miscommunication and server's behavior, we decided not to tip them this time.

When server saw we gave no tips, she said "NO TIPS?????"
"Was anything wrong??"

When we were going to speak about the bad experience, she interrupted and said "it's ok" and WALKED AWAYü§£
I wonder why she asked us if she is not going to listen to us.

We stood up and went outside of the restaurant, and she never says thank you.

We couldn't enjoy our meal at all because of the bad experience. WON'T be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMj1pXTISptBEWEn3NYWdCWanHbL4oXqnTHYBqo&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"Uros Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqZKUGj61BfmTYu8vecdYC7cNoaJsQnfWJB3zipm50mUOPG3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Japanese‚Äôs restaurant has a good variety of sushi choices on their menu. I ordered sushi rolls , and other things from menu and everything was very tasty and fresh.
Pricing is fair ,not too expensive and waitress was very polite so I‚Äôll definitely come back.
All recommendations for this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMK5F8RgXraZhkqG9TOfycuu11buc0B-IPkBPnQ&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2024-4-4"},{"Name":"Djordje Kojic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBL6vcGYM0P3feyhqJkWM8uZeZP_Q7F0JmFh9MDsvKIRzJtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small little place in a strip mall. Just went in for a quick meal. It doesn‚Äôt look like much, but the quality of the food was amazing. I was very pleasantly surprised. Way better quality then I expected going into the place. The nigiri was amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3IlHYlAdGeHSjUXE-4Lk7E1GAxsEcKpFJ1Oct&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2024-4-4"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They have a good variety of sushi choices on their menu but I found their sushi rice lacked the usual plumpness, sweetness, and vinegar flavor other places have. The sushi was not bad, but overall, quite average. For the price you pay, I have had nicer and tastier sushi at the same price or cheaper. It still does the job of satisfying a sushi craving though. Like a standard neighborhood sushi place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeHpD8Qrbh2ezSqIV-f9pTI-p9eEIOTrM9pHxE&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2022-10-7"},{"Name":"Leona Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmB6XMzxTi6G9GEmyD0MJjB6nkqYOP7GVBTMUakDrRUolumXkH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Perhaps one of the best authentic Japanese meals we have had recently. You will find some unique and traditional Japanese dishes here that many Japanese restaurants will not carry nowadays: real tobiko, ikura, masago, anago, aji, etc. They were fresh and sweet. We ordered these in the form of temaki sushi. I couldn't believe that how generous that they put the tobiko, ikura on top! It was a real deal for me. The wasabi is made of the real one, not the mimic horseradish. The staffs were really friendly.
I understand the frustration that some of the other reviewers expressed - e.g. minimum charge of $15 per person. When you have kiddos it seems unreasonable. However, for two of us, we easy ate over $80 there (ate too much, now groaning), the $15/p seems not a difficult thing.
My favourite: tori karaage (fried Juicy boneless chicken), Tobiko nigiri sushi (flying fish roes), masago nigiri sushi (smelt fish roes), aji butterly fries, dragon rolls.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO50I8hjv88AxZ0A7I3a6Io1fcEeUCHlCM4aDAI&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Rebecca P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOtv1z9oQXsu_j8G9uE8jVQGZlbdGZfOgnrsP8gOev0iFfifM3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very delicious and fresh sushi! You can definitely taste the quality. The servers are very friendly. Overall great experience.

A very small place, recommend to book a reservation! I would definitely keep coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQWRLRvQuM5UOpudvP7FoQNFiUeBHB_C_5UEen&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2022-3-16"},{"Name":"Nathan Gock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHkNE3wp0BHPmjWdgFbhh1J2W__TRTD91hRVxAd_Wa5elpxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Japanese owned and operated sushi spot on New West. We really like the Uni Ikura Don, and the Aji Tataki was also delicious. All the nigiri we ordered were great as well. Service was also very nice!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6_YkXHdk-ZPsGzGLNfNZHYcId1y49nc3M0JBl&fid=0x0:0xebc91fe3fe1ee168"],"When":"2021-9-4"}]

Service was slow and disorganized, as we didn‚Äôt know which server was helping us.  Throughout the night we saw the same thing happen where customers were not getting menus, water, or orders taken .  The only this was the manager was good and tried to fix things but he really needs to train the staff properly .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBkSEilfqQdXVWiUqaJO8lB7TxsXHX-37Ov0aW&fid=0x0:0x60775b10bf5d551c"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Esther W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ44_CjQ6-wehLPc33Ng17kPOWOSFrXqo3jg5WgP7CtwNUYUeR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Disgusting amount of flies on the wall as circled in my photo. Makes me worry about how clean the food is. The scallops were not as pictured in the photo. There was 5 in the menu that they shown, but in real life, I was only served 4.

The remaining scallops were overcooked and very chewy. The size of the scallops were significantly smaller than pictures as well.

The food was underwhelming and expensive. I would not recommend coming back here, although the server was nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZb06Dgno413mSijdKkL7S4_cvv9wPpU-Kakhl&fid=0x0:0x60775b10bf5d551c"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Julian Hui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXva6nMTps59_gZysueK6_Z4Rf3q6G-hVl-STfHAFEObUz1ODMSqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was great. Very attentive and server was checking in frequently to ensure eveything was going well.
Food was decent.  We ordered the Tartufati gnocchi but the truffle flavor was underwhelming and was disappointed considered it was one of the most expensive dish without any meat. Gnocchi tasted fresh with great fluffy consistency though. We also ordered the Tagliatelle Papalina.  The flavor was great but the pasta was not al dente and it was overly cooked and it was way too soft.  Overall experience was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5xVbSNezTOc5xT_BASy5pzc8ut3MoCJnUd2t1&fid=0x0:0x60775b10bf5d551c"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Sandra Bao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCFDxhJJiWfK1A7jrtmOnJj84ihz5DRnzbJb1wpxZG21ZEY8Oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I‚Äôm writing this review because I hope people can stop being fooled by the 4.4 scores on their Google Maps.

Food - Food was horrible, especially the two pasta dishes we got- They are not just flavourless but they simply taste bad. I‚Äôm not a good cook but I‚Äôm sure I can make better pasta than the food they served us‚Ä¶ They have 4 dessert options on the menu, but we were told they only had Tiramisu and Affogato. The so called ‚ÄúTiramisu‚Äù tasted awful and overly sweet.

Environment: The moment we walked into the restaurant, we could smell washroom‚Ä¶ There were also so many fruit flies flying around us during our dinner. Though the space was wide and my husband and I could enjoy a quieter space (because there were only 2 other groups in the restaurant who sat in different corners), you can tell this restaurant is aged but not well maintained.

Service: The lady who took our order and served us was the only good thing about this restaurant.

Sometimes if the environment of a restaurant is not clean but the food is tasty, we would probably be okay with it, but this restaurant I really can‚Äôt justify the $100 we paid for the poor quality of food we got. Will never be back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkWcoDpegiWwDZcoeHm2OAcNrJBJUFAZ_LUPPW&fid=0x0:0x60775b10bf5d551c"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Roxsan Bargayo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPXVNuCjS5kalz_g8kM1jbSLRYWdH0q6i7AsZkp_K1h5TcRWis=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their Calamarata Profumo Di Mare pasta is truly a standout among seafood dishes I've experienced. The flavor is simply divine! To top it off, I relished every moment, thanks to the fantastic service and delightful atmosphere. ü§§","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOs77XfuEQJq-rD54L32GrcMXOo3q2rJ_-QVsD3&fid=0x0:0x60775b10bf5d551c"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Vince Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIh1Bs882K37cbDDZYd4kfA59hdXMTzPce_oh3-IJYn9tkT8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went there for dinner with great expectations.  Sadly, it didn‚Äôt turn out that way. Service was good and food came out quick.

The food was nicely presented but everything was extremely salty.  We were drinking water for hours after we got home.

We ordered the meatballs and 3 different pasta dishes. All were very salty to the point that my kids didn‚Äôt want to eat anymore.

The bread that was served was also very stale.  This is one of the easiest things to execute during service and they couldn‚Äôt even do it right.

I hope they are able to fix their issues as it appears to have been a very good restaurant years ago.

It's just great. It's always outfront of Columbia skytrain Station, but on Sundays I think they are closed. Best falafel wrap","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYW3ZqwRg4YjYykVTEyA4AwL4byNRSa9ogOQS-&fid=0x0:0xc1f36f889546b7e5"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Anneke Feuermann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU91ogL8zpaW8vhZgYj1lOCcP6dZXgn8d0AI33U5okEgEtA26-Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Marvin‚Äôs Falafel is not just good food - it‚Äôs good service, too. Over the course of a year we have lived in New West, and have eaten MF food as much as we can. The family who runs it is so kind, genuine, and caring. They ask about your day, they make small talk with you, and when we told them we were moving away, they teared up. Always working with a smile and eager to provide us with a sample or two, they are the absolute best. If MF opened a brick & mortar we would send all of our friends and family there every single night. Amazing food, amazing value, outstanding service. If you have not gone yet, this is your sign. You will not regret supporting this family business and having one of the best meals of your life.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOer1ZJh9c9s_H0ZM_cY0iXqyUvzSm6ItR0EcH9&fid=0x0:0xc1f36f889546b7e5"],"When":"2023-11-24"},{"Name":"Adele Shiphrah Gorovenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWl-L9s4B7RbfAOcGiMMsPrGgLbrX5K6RArFMNd8-RXWaWXDmue=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's so refreshing to enjoy authentic food from people who know how to make it! The falafels were definitely made with love.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBJtDH1Mc4hJPjBOZJQb3rv1gB0KChuYIMp4mF&fid=0x0:0xc1f36f889546b7e5"],"When":"2024-3-4"},{"Name":"Patt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUmP4t_e1KDxqzOIGol8UhC9LV0_4HteMTwKPEOl6DT-KB5sDm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVED the food! I tried asking what the sauce is, but it seems to be a trade secret, which is understandable.

I got the chicken plate. It was hefty, lots of protein on top. No complaints, it was a really good meal. Plus, the server was very polite and friendly. I noted that they also do Vegan options, which I didn't really order, but felt I should mention, in case anyone wants to know. Feel like this may be a gem outside Columbia Station. [{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a new location of Shiok Singapore Restaurant.  It's a family restaurant.  We need to support our local and family restaurant.
The new bright renovation, the food, service, air-condition, the patio and the price are unbeatable.
If you never been to this restaurant, you must have a try.
The unbeatable price are $13.95 for a curry chicken with rice, $3 for a iced coffee or tea.  The taste and the portion are good.
May I have a little advice.  If they make the order plastic sheet in English dish names, maybe a big help for the new customers.
So we don't need to look the big menu then go back to the order sheet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyDO-6uZRz2S-vMj3-A8uGYw7EVbQCMnH9VdFU&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmgoFQrGMjTU1qQTL4G07bvioF513c9HVkJY_GKQpIXUgF4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a small space, but was pleasantly surprised by the prices, food and the friendly owner. The owner came and helped us decide on what to get and gave recommendations. He was very friendly and accommodating, and the food tasted good as well.
We ordered the laksa, the curry chicken, the curry fish as well as the skewers.
Would highly recommend you give it a shot! New west needed a Singaporean cuisine and this is the best spot right now!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI7CsVEhX9oekBJtMimnR-PtPE-BO2j4Dw7O3Z&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Êü¥Áöì‰ªÅ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDHLhzhIePFnKjokxmRTW35ZkREa_RSNsAfy7IPpC-D6Q7n4Yj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a very nice Singaporean restaurant. The food is delicious and very Singaporean, the service is good and the price is reasonable. It is a relaxing place to sit down and eat, highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMx8JUvilu5lKVAR3QVvOITeDAAlRoAjmpn3SU9&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came at 6pm Sunday, the little restaurant was busy but the service was fast & efficient. The premises is clean & neat. We had satay beef & chicken skewers, roti prata to share, hainanese chicken rice & bandung (pink rose water) for me, beef rendang & calamasi drink for my husband. The food was delicious at good prices. My chicken was super tender and I love the rice that is cooked in chicken broth, it has very nice ginger aroma. That pink rose drink is yummy at $3! Shiok Canteen reminds me of those food stalls in Singapore (without flights and heat, their AC works very well haha). Will come back to try their laksa & chedol (our next table had them and they looked mouth watering). I like the way water is filled in continuously and the friendly owner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONwLIJt6JVei6TY9wnr8XQYdmtWlC8EZ0Ljg1I&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Cheuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViyaLSrOR53wIdh-1tPL1EO-fv4jJiDA_NDJQYVAHprBRcIndGIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely my go to place for Singaporean food, cannot be more authentic than Shiok.  Glad they opened a location in new West. Food is excellent, laksa has the same taste I had when I was living in Singapore.  Hainan chicken rice is very good as well, chicken is so soft my son loves it!  Service is excellent, always makes sure you are taken care of but never too much as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUcUDGfodSKBjMqtJp_2rPLwuK8rA6IgF8Oi39&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Jessie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPwp36N1ftgRNl5Ql-GlVvcrKKUkfRjvh7SllcIwq6UnTH7Yaq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ordered the seafood laksa, beef puff pastry, chicken rice and calamansi drink! everything came out pretty quickly and the family was super attentive and great with their service!
the food was very yummy and satisfying ‚ò∫Ô∏è

will definitely be coming back in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJxFro8tWqQgtwFAMn1SqTrkF5i_3oieMA6Avc&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Kasumi Okajima (Kas)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3m9Zzz5V40ZOlaImUkn3ZQp6STmmVav3AD_8yRA8CBB-Hy749=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The owner there has great recommendations so you can ask him. [{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A fun place to try Brazilian street food. The Pastels are tasty with good melted cheese pull in the middle. The assorted deep fried bites were good with mixtures of ham and cheese, chicken, etc. They sell drinks like matte and guarana. The food is on the heavier and greasy side but unique and tasty and good for an occasional treat. They also sell some Brazilian groceries there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJiOrAcrWq514B2xp-vWKX2q45DVkYSoaJ21Vm&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2024-10-4"},{"Name":"Asif Ali Rahman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNaegjRmNO50bHqqeLJtzO0MH4x4EfVRHgZ8LaeHetSvlquLkr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This has been my favourite restaurant until now when I met a rude young girl today. It‚Äôs Sunday and 5:30 pm. She was the one without glasses. She was literally dictating my order. I had a guest tonight from out of town who asked me if I could recommend a good restaurant and I brought him here to have shrimp no. 8. I ordered for both of us when she suddenly asked my friend if he eats shrimp what I had just ordered. My friend doesn‚Äôt normally eat shrimp but he wanted to try. The girl insisted that your friend doesn‚Äôt want shrimp embarrassing me in the process. Then I was ordering the bigger one no. 8. She insisted that my friend can also get the smaller one because the bigger one is expensive. So my friend who likes to eat more ended up eating half of my order too. My friend hated what he had ordered and his comments were that this is a terrible restaurant.

The shrimp that I ordered had very few shrimps in it. Terrible food.  I‚Äôm not coming back to this restaurant again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhyp2Im-TVoOCLWtMUIhYuhZnv_9cFmO5xTcc9&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Katia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoejtYSJ-c7Ynia18FuXvHbd745iN29dWOGkI4LU_5lixNeywE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great pastel de queijo! Felt so good to be able to have a little taste of home again. The bolinha de queijo was a little too bland for me, a little salt would have helped. My friend got coxinha de frango and said it was good.

I‚Äôd love to see more vegetarian options of pastel like cheese with oregano and tomatoes (pizza style)

Prices are high considering what I‚Äôm used to paying for this meal in Brazil but knowing everything is imported is understandable. Unfortunately it‚Äôs not the place I‚Äôd be able to go to and have more than one pastel.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-_-5au7vaLvlem5OMcRxf9HYAtdTz4dEK5SK4&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2022-11-19"},{"Name":"Tracy Adina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICXGY0Ftc1fiXva9t_vLaLmPB0I6d-MMI6HH1tL-B4fIYa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried for the first time yesterday. It was sooo delicious and crispy!

We had the plain cheese puffs, which were soo yummy and goey inside. We also had the beef especial pasteis. The crust was super thin and flaky and the filling was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUH2W4Jxmujl-34SA6Af5q8awXimWxNBYOIrc&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2023-4-25"},{"Name":"L P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2-s14ft5BiaBgf6wD69hCD-Fd8SrdejFGLneEQD2V5-MuDoLU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place used to be amazing, especially a couple of years ago. Sadly, it seems like they‚Äôve made some changes. The meat pastel now uses a lower-quality, oily cut of ground beef, and the palmito pastel, which used to be just like the ones in Brazil, hardly has any palmito anymore. It‚Äôs disappointing to see the quality isn‚Äôt what it used to be.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jossana Haas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9HS1fZakd9ATG0kA5vPRp33X316DVs8TMI4cwGuykQPfD6mqz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pastel and coxinha! Fresh, tasty and great customer service! A bit pricey, but that‚Äôs the price to pay when you miss food from your home country‚Ä¶ it not only fills up the belly but also the heart üíõüíöüíô","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6v8_kYKhYU9R5fCMP3fs9zVsxKhvPMopbo8sN&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2021-7-7"},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I liked the texture of the crisply fried dough in my beef and cheese pastel, but I found it pricy based on the sparse amount of filling and it was a bit bland tasting. It was also a very long wait (15 mins) despite the fact that we were the only ones in the joint. I had to inquire about my order and the cashier explained that my wife‚Äôs chicken pie was still being prepared and it was delayed because their gravy machine was broken. By the time I received my pastel, it was luke warm, but the chicken was hot. The chicken tasted like it was from a can though. I had also wanted to try their fresh pressed sugar cane juice but alas, that juice press was also broken. Not sure I would give this place a second try. Maybe for the fresh sugar cane juice as I miss fresh pressed sugar cane juice!  I would have given 1 star but the cashier seemed very apologetic for the delay, so I moved it up one star.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjTagkmTHmqdJK6fXllB7UcqMt6BfcER31AKQE&fid=0x0:0xb0170e8318381d0b"],"When":"2021-11-8"},{"Name":"Julie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6EagigylvL8HL0PYbonoE3Mv8ji3wWv7NdsGCZfLbfxhVVvyx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place always looks empty so I thought the food wasn't good but after passing by for so many years, I finally decided to go inside and the food is delicious! My husband got the carne seca and I got the calabresa and the pastry itself was tasty on its own and the filling so flavourful in a good way! I will go back to try every filling. Please check this place out! Warning: dining in will have you smelling like oil after 15 minutes, haha.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Old review: Lovely cafe. Great coffee. Only thing is parking which is very limited. I would NOT recommend coming to this cafe","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKAE80SfA9yiPdW3_nbaK9M1fG8gCAv_v-RHLl&fid=0x0:0x65b2570531ca3901"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Sophie Shrestha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZAKUGWb_NlP6bN7qxGZ8yi9_nfPCc7EaBTcSgZePzdV6vxEpL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute, lowkey cafe in New West! user_reviews: [{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow, this place is pretty awesome! It was my first time at this pizzeria, and it was amazing. I had the chicken heist pizza, which was pretty good. The service was good too. Friendly staff. The atmosphere was excellent. The place is a pizzeria and a game place. You can eat pizza with friends and family while playing a whole bunch of different kinds of board games. I would definitely recommend  coming here.five out of five stars. I really enjoyed my time here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCvlBkwpK7XrqHUyo2oPGUOIjSfR5KwHrILIi6\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Maddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXq_lMfr3DxCG3QMSSXrsIOugoFQ2p8xP2z6Kvl56AUDcql_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cool restaurant with good food and a great selection of games!! The Vul Kar pizza was delicious especially with added pineapple. The portions were big and they had a lot of good drink options. It was quite busy and a little hot inside but otherwise we had a great time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOsGHob05rQLrtLrWFoa-8WpS8Q1tnsl6SSVh1\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"Dan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6Vpad3zmd_bRS_NRyMDg5xHn355DE6cSY0nXB1CDQJfi5a5o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza was good, made fresh from the oven. Tiramisu on the other hand, was not so good. It was dry, I had to down it with water. Besides food, they have a wide selection of board games. We spent hours playing games there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFb0hBfL8DXVLQnDU4K0T72zBTShoKvPAOjT3j\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-6-29"},{"Name":"Tanvi E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXx-ES0DjbI2Lh_4scJ5ImMqu0DXCb-cPxW5hBwsAQ8oKFOQ38=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was quite busy and extremely loud. There were only 3 servers with big groups on multiple tables. The server came to us in about 20 minutes after we were seated. Not her fault, just understaffed. The food was good, but it was too noisy for not such a big space. Rating it based on the food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLTX2REUNnNF5H6q_HhcBSzszK-6uSKNDB-rfB\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, pricing \u0026 service, nothing to complain about. They have a big selection of board games which diners can use. It seems like staff are not rushing customers out after the meal like many restaurants these days. They used high quality cheese, which we both love.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwTWHd0EX7J4eOP1v0N5jkh38XcN_RdreDmhEk\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-2-2"},{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"One of the few restaurants that also offer board games. Good unique concept for customers to be entertained while eating. Large variety of games to play.\n\nThe service is quite slow. The servers did not even acknowledge that our water was empty and we had to keep asking several times. In terms of the food, our pizza came out at a decent time. Definitely have a lot of choices, however I ended up ordering a safe choice (Hawaiian).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcWgKt8IJlP-bZGYqbV5ANppPblCRRfpUgQV-K\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Sunny Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoEvkuYabe3D808e6JGZNrZuYbs0Hk57aqzylF_NjY63wfZvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a lovely spot to hang out, catch up with friends, and play one or several of their large selection of board games. Pizza is great, pasta portions are large, prices are comparable to other establishments, but there is no fee to play any of their games. The staff have been lovely, warm, and inviting.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Akshita Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6wgZMu-cjbsBT2ad4hC21-hyvycSFx7odboIAaezCz6WVHKsAug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing food, really enjoyed the board games. Pretty cool place to hang out with friends. A lot of vegetarian and vegan options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlae7ulqQjD3fkPlwEHFw-CWOeAxGi3doY186y\u0026fid=0x0:0x26cd686a98dcaf92"],"When":"2024-6-25"}]

[{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem and heartwarming dining experience. The owner or staff, both of them, are very enthusiastic about their food and super kind. They have somehow perfected frying fries. The fries are made fresh to order and they give you a heaping amount with the perfect seasoning. Like, if there was a perfect definition of a French fry, they serve it here; hot, fresh, crispy outside, fluffy inside, bursting with potato flavour! Who would have thought this mall food court place served such good fries????!!!

As for the Philly cheesesteak, it tastes very homemade and hearty with really meaty beef. The beef dip is also hearty with lots of beef. The Philly cheesesteak and beef dip were both good but not gourmet or anything, however, they remind you of granny‚Äôs home cooking made with love. That‚Äôs what this place gives you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoYxU8KEyQVwS8jXtB6siQTzziTL8azkP82-iK&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Ian Grimsdick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVNAwbGbAg7iHFZCH2ZcRPNQCqhdrLGjma3MI6N7NMRmpkI8DArQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best food court restaurant in the entire lower mainland.  A combination of guilty pleasure food and grilled options that make you feel good. The staff are friendly and helpful, even when it's really busy which it often is as students will come here for lunch. I just had the Cajun pork which was marinated in a great, just spicy enough marinate and grilled on the spot, served with rice and veggies. You talk to people who go there and they'll rave about pretty much everything on the menu.  This is the kind of place you want to see succeed because they seem like genuinely good guys and they're passionate about the food.  And they have a great system to keep things flowing even when it's busy.  Thanks gentlemen.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely wonderful Philly Cheesesteak. Beefy peppery flavour with just the right amount of melted cheese to bind into the sandwich with sweet grilled onions and peppers. Fries were fresh out of the oil fryer seasoned with the perfect amount of salt and black pepper. Really good value for quality and quantity. The guys behind the counter cooking were really nice to boot and struck up a genuine conversation. Great choice to get something to eat if you‚Äôre in this mall food court‚Ä¶scratch that‚Ä¶I‚Äôd make this food stall the main destination for my reason to visit this mall!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOr8pa9D0h1Vjj6a0lyxFKJKRFcoXmGEGGubjsA&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Amanda V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZOLydh5sGAptUXnunY5WEfbl7N6dKLnwlzx-ViawgM6fOfXAmPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wide variety of food on the menu, literally something for everyone! We tried the beef fries & cajun pork, good taste! Owner is lovely as well, and they have slushies with free refill! Such a great summer option. Highly recommended hidden gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO91xmjvez1wI5XUtpco4xy1Co4AsvyEsKR53-w&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Patrice Ayana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOllg0k09Gc0JobV45f-oVFUTx6IqK6OZGrSkFW1cGk9xCvPTsOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Joined a food group and I saw a few people mentioning this place so I decided to try it. I ordered the Philly cheesesteak sandwich with fries and it was delicious! I also ordered the loaded Philly cheesesteak fries. I will definitely be back again! Excellent service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGwQ1OYhDO0aRh7bksySOS84lyxlcEZZogzpZ_&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Daniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvd6-q0LFLnT6Fjanc2ymc9JLptLuzcaQqNrOdzOGpx9n_bEE6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Owner is incredibly friendly and passionate. Order times are pretty fast and you get to watch him cook.

I ordered the pulled pork sandwich combo. The fries are some of the best I've had, well seasoned and crispy. The sandwich was great. The combination of toasted bread with sauce and juicy pulled pork was soo delicious.

Overall, service and food 10/10. Can't go wrong","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMO8otfQ_-A5clRjzTQHXzLusOH0JUN71KGzo7O&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"Bonnie Somers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZUWA-6wmQn1fXY7hj9EJECrGoeopb6z_FXpQjZ_RE3JsAMU8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grilled chicken is excellent! good portion, fantastic service, recommend !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1MVPnSd8jDssGk8lR2OXzd3sEdX_dDmDQdZRA&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Sahar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX78XZJ0-0JszsjUnipV__49pbD8R8fMYHiB37wWppP0GEXbB5u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grill n More is the BEST fast food restaurant at Royal City Centre. Mr.chef is very friendly and courteous. The food that I ordered ( Philly cheese steak) was so tasty and delicious too. üòã
** huge portion and reasonable price.
I 100% recommend this place and I am ready to try different food from this menu in near future..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeI6vE7GjE-F7zoEPyBGHBDeAp4ol9EzlgD4R4&fid=0x0:0x1ecb9130fdc39fb"],"When":"2023-2-28"}]

We had the smalls and they were still rather large in size so be mindful when ordering as this is not food to be wasted and enjoyed. I decided to go and grab a poutine from the spud shack. Every time I go there it great as they have delicious poutines, great service and stuff. I ordered myself the medium size of the night market. Which is fries, curds, and gravy topped with ginger beef, spicy mayo, kimchi, crispy wontons, and green onions. It is always a good treat to have on a cold day, but especially after a nice long walk home. [{"Name":"C L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFSCt_t74XiqlEdz6jDYOHmtwc4pgb3Fve6nsF3wEBwwz9hl0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Unpretentious neighbourhood favourite in downtown New Westminster. This restaurant is part of the Westminster Centre Shopping Centre so parking is easy. Google Maps leads you right to the lot! We went on a Saturday night and it was already packed with locals at 6:30pm. They got so busy that they missed our orders. However, the server was apologetic and rushed to get our orders out. They serve traditional Greek fare such as souvlaki but there are daily chef specials on a whiteboard too.  Homey and comforting; it is easy to see why this restaurant has loyal patrons.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSOt6nAyeyowRanTZK9s6lPYrJB_Hhfgs48qSo&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"NDS Investments","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVikPs6WOuTzc-E92-sZ1BLaCA6XPNBLrLbmLXnMK-Mmkbrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered through Uber eats and regretted it as soon as we opened the container...food was not appealing, bland, overall...just stale....waste of $60 plus

With our experience, we would not order from this establishment again.

Cannot rate service or atmosphere as we did not dine in","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEtpMInjQNr6rxpkE75Rku2uL8UqBeWr5a54_U&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Feyona McKenna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZDDipdNdQOlJp1dg4n7g1mc0Smm73l7RifmYSNiXg-VGEyg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My first visit to Yiannis Greek Taverna in New Westminster was a pleasant surprise. Located inside a mall, the restaurant offers plenty of free parking and a separate entrance from the outside. Initially, the small door from the mall and the dim lighting made us unsure if it was open. My daughter even asked, ‚ÄúIs it open? Why is it so dark in there?‚Äù However, once inside, we were greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance.

Despite it being 6 PM on a bustling Saturday, we managed to snag one of the last tables. Our server was exceptionally friendly and accommodating, although she did forget to place our order and my daughter‚Äôs apple juice. After a 40-minute wait, she apologized sincerely, assured us she would expedite our order, and offered us complimentary dessert as a gesture of goodwill.

When our food finally arrived, it was worth the wait. The portions were generous, and I ended up taking some home. I had the roast lamb, which was incredibly tender and fell off the bone. My daughter, a notoriously picky eater, enjoyed her salmon in tomato sauce, possibly because of the long wait. My husband had the lamb souvlaki, and our friend tried the potato-crusted cod‚Äîboth dishes were delicious.

To top off our meal, our server brought us ek mek, a Greek dessert, on the house. Despite my usual preference for chocolate desserts, I was pleasantly surprised by how much I enjoyed it.

Overall, Yiannis Greek Taverns exceeded our expectations, and I wouldn‚Äôt hesitate to return the next time I‚Äôm craving Greek cuisine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7PQfPHYYweZZsaIMbYUDpVrWoFnfl9YSzp__W&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Bob Ilapogu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXD-elaNhBNUvlaxka6eecnsUdCevkSM7CivjrbdDP1sf2qzFrO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a medical appointment nearby, with about 40 minutes to spare. We saw the sign for Yianni's and thought we'd give it a try. We were greeted immediately by Kelsey. After explaining that we were in a bit of a rush, she assured us that it would take less than 15 minutes to receive our food. In fact, it took only 10! The prices were extremely reasonable and the food was quite tasty. Kelsey was perhaps the most friendly and efficient server we've ever had. We will definitely return in the future, as we'd like to try more of the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuQMi8qNOegbOtqemVM55SCqnGB04sm3b_BzY&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Ashraf Elhassan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuLkzBLPu9ua4RE40nOlcxoyN63gwKQwJa-XbekTX0jza_GlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Lamb shoulder was amazing
Service was very good, thank you Erin, we will definitely come back to try another recipe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipML7ls0RSchsql1GcgNyp0H5ZKha5DtQVScRZgv&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Geetika Hora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuNXRgll-y86-Lux7G-wc87KBo-i7d7XePhOGrz1Fb2zDBfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered roast lamb meal for take out. This was my second time getting food from them. First time was dine in last year and I recall it was good back then. Not sure what changed. Meat felt so stale, we couldn't take a second bite. Maybe because it was Monday dinner and they are closed on Tuesday which I didn't know, they were probably clearing out old stuff. Salad was nowhere close to authentic greek salad. Carrots were the frozen baby carrots. Definitely spoiled our dinner, had to throw it all out. Never gonna order here again or I will lose my interest in Greek food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6kFEqbhrn0HzX1VHDlIh66m_RONxO6cfLV2Xs&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Seem like there dishes have gotten smaller but still very tasty.. Service has gotten slow or she forgot to get it. Had to ask twice for mint sauce for my lamb dish.. then I had to get up and ask the kitchen for it.. don‚Äôt get me wrong it‚Äôs the first time they did this to me.. service is usually really good..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcSkx-2qFrBfS2I-zcX-VStrkTfGlcxX50c1xp&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"KC CLAY FLOWERS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjHlWzIim_FuzOFm9RWi0CgeKWQj7ySiZICNdORO2eQ9BAXZxWAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good food fresh cooked and friendly staff good atmosphere . Love this place and highly recommend for Greek cuisine lover another best place in New Westminster here ..
very convenient you also can park inside of the building behind London drug ..
inside the resturant have the restroom accessible for handicap people..
Yannis Greek Taverna is well known Resturant for this area you will love it !!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHkvc4oGN2ZyEUtXDp5bhu9X2M1ZcF9lZaNVHA&fid=0x0:0xaa8584956b498880"],"When":"2024-2-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered drinks, waffle nachos and wings. Although I enjoyed salt and pepper, I found the buffalo wings to be a bit soggy. I found the staff to be very friendly and attentive. I really recommend the place especially for late night drinks and snacks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2fY8JhX6tC_lC7BmtGZ0As0ZEByfCi163Fxhb&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Kate Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjE4MSAa0c4Uqc8iOt1LfqIkJDL1ULa2Z17gRh4YDWMExQ1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I heard they had a discount for people celebrating their birthdays so I decided to try this place out.

The place is big with lots of outdoor seating. Almost nowhere to park there except a few paid spots here and there.

When we came in we were greeted quickly and our server came to take orders fairly quickly as well. Then it all went downhill from there.

We ordered the prime rib medium rare. Although the color was great, the top of the steak was all dried from sitting there too long after cutting. The meat was also tough. The soup was broccoli and bacon and it was quite salty and the croutons were stale. We got the lattice fries which everyone raved about. The fries were ok but seasoning was only on a few.

We also ordered the seafood pesto fettuccine which claims it has lobster. It came with a lot of tiny shrimps and imitation crab. No lobster meat to be found. I thought for almost $30 for the pasta, there'd be some lobster bits. The garlic bread was good and the pesto sauce was delicious though.

When we were done, we wanted to get the bill and pay. Since this bar only allows one server per table, no other servers were willing to serve us. We waited over 20 min for our server to notice us looking at her. She was too busy at the drink bar making drinks. We got the bill, the -$30 was taken off for the birthday discount, we paid, and the server quickly just went away. No happy birthday or any goodbye greeting. She was just too busy.

Don't think we'll be returning here as regular customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA5_-zgUj6YIJrCcdVvatTtnqiciOW39MU9G70&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Sandeep Patil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkfias45QhgRJ8x-jbidsLsdJf1V8WF5xtbY2Qhjx8BL_-hxwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located at convenient spot next to river Fraser and river parks, Kelly's allow you to relax down after a long walk by riverside of New Westminster. After soaking in the setting sun, watching trains pass over the river walk down in this Irish pub where attendants are dressed up to give the Irish vibe. You get plenty of cocktail options to choose from and while you are waiting for it you can solve the riddles on the menu card. The building gives a cabin feeling and always busy. The patio is another added advantage of this establishment where you can sip in your cocktail with potato skins while enjoying the cool breeze from river. Cost is okish compared to the location and vibe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQ-d34AOAzKeCK7Tu4DLiARxNpgZjeWWeOPG6j&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Madhukar Pathak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfDv7dCarikgkYCyK9sr2IdxEdH9H5SUBEbUg3puQPsZH5UJ3ADw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Loved this place !!
Been there couple of times already with a positive feedback each time.
Unfortunately, yesterday was not that time. The Lamb burger that was ordered had a hair in it. Thankfully it was noticed after one bite and the our Server was happy to change the order. But, that ruined the streak of great times in this pub.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAoGtTbSAczK4k3Cn_So460TdkXgXPL6_A8H6x&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Moira Casey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqH8ArDou9s_zoBtlaH2uA9ZPMDv3j1_WOTzaJd-UkxMhhAnEjxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food, drinks and service were all very good. Huge restaurant/pub with upstairs seating as well. Good place to meet family or friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9XlfaPyFUvinN_JsznCUYDLWF4l2fCXyxPPJq&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"kavya rawal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVF1Y6oHOVELURyrsxj6F02ztQQoo7vLbcyOfavbREk6dJ0XxFu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first time coming in for a birthday special. And everything was beyond expectations. literally the best vegetarian burger I‚Äôve ever had. Onion rings were so fresh, and the strawberry mojito was just perfect. Our server Abbee was so friendly, walked us through vegetarian options and told us a little bit about the restaurant. Such a pleasant experience!
Fun fact: Building is 100 years old!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpbqYBfPmB15Lrka_gLShxv7bMQYfm-lmxMyD3&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited Kelly O‚ÄôBryan‚Äôs in New Westminster and had a fantastic experience! The Irish restaurant/bar has a cozy atmosphere inside and is located in a beautiful building. We loved that they played great 90s tunes, even while showing sports on the screens. The prices for cocktails were also super reasonable. Overall, we highly recommend Kelly O‚ÄôBryan‚Äôs for a fun and relaxed night out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leo Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhrqhlkToJU2ktCM__Ybm4QiDKDhUsqHcN5nJSXQE6aFyTEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First of all, I'm not a pub guy and I was there only for their b-day deal. It's really noisy but that's expected as it's a pub. Ordered their prime rib and the Cali club. Both were just mediocre at best. However, their fries were the highlight of the meal, I found that to be the most tasty out of everything we ordered.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKLhyhZ_sTbA2lhyf5q8aoM2jAxWwQSzxTk1YS&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2023-11-15"}]

[{"Name":"Kab Kbaas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5U0xr3upvQTURbvXCvcu5mgHu9kAs3kt9vv_C4iuqaE8mdtRkEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Captain's oven pizza strikes again! This is the new edition to this up and coming franchise. The pizza here at this location is as excellent as it is at the other locations.

Everything from the time you enter the restaurant, to your order being taken, to the actual taste of this delicious pizza is a treat!

If you haven't eaten at this or at the other Captain's Oven pizza outlets, what are you waiting for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV70YShrbRJD2YqmIe8uPFYnLjCouLZk2yun9-&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Johnny Hsu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnJCpeAf_rNo3J-P8wYYkAus79ikEYQpAwrpY7-h_p6gndGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great new place!   Awesome pizza and everything tasted so fresh.   We tried some of the veggie options, of which there were many.   Really great menu and there are so many choices that sounded delicious, it was very difficult to choose.  Will have to come back to try some others.   We had a Caprese and a Chef's Special.  Both were delicious.  We had meatballs in marinara too but forgot to take a pic.  So good!   Tiramisu for dessert was a perfect way to finish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsi10IKu8HCHISk-3zxG1fymIk_lnnWdcApuWq&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"sanjin ramovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWao3NCDoBfu96Y6YVIck2LSuOpB-Wbt71v94bbUF_9zLIh6UJQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, helpful staff.

We bought 4 pizzas here today, and loved them. Their pizza was delicious, with great crust, quality cheese and fresh ingredients. Adults loved the Capriciossa and Mexican, and the kids thought that the Hawaiian was the best.

Will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2j1Z61i-gDrA4Uci5bKE31joE1CKYWx6RtZ35&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Ketron Casio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwBIJbgGs0I8DkEZa5zp4-cK7c-6EXQ_EoY7PCgD78FZmG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to share with you an incredible pizza place that I recently discovered in New west . I have ordered from them twice now, and I must say, it has been the best pizza I‚Äôve had so far. The quality of the ingredients, the flavors, and the overall experience have truly exceeded my expectations.

One of the things that truly stood out to me was the outstanding customer service provided by the staff. The owners of the pizzeria are incredibly nice and friendly, making the whole dining experience even more enjoyable. They pay attention to every detail and ensure that their customers are well taken care of.

I highly recommend giving this pizza place a try. I believe you will love it just as much as I do. Whether you are a fan of traditional pizzas or prefer something more unique, they have a wide variety of options to choose from. I am confident that you will be impressed by the quality and taste of their pizzas.

If you decide to give it a try, please let me know your thoughts. I would love to hear about your experience. I am sure you will not be disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jmbstat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4TODiBsftPq9OFVr5nwW3ykAdRY2fPCqtIkp3MV3W0L87sjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dropped by during their soft opening and was quite surprised with the options available. Captains oven pizza is a family owned, wood fire oven pizza joint, with a long list of flavors! I tried their Mexicana picante which has a kick of heat. Falvours were delicous, and has free sauces available during dine in, the price was very fair for the size, quality and toppings. The open kitchen shows their extreme cleanliness and the staff were very friendly! Defintiley a must try before they get busy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcCOkd-7QAoVhGGHUUUwSYE7kVZdNWwrtHSeNB&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Craig Afonso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8bAv0onJPry9osSMLvfTocBp6OFdo_ZdcbZOzskU82vSV_DZa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When it comes to pizzas, Captain‚Äôs Oven never fails to impress! We decided to stick to the classics this time, and they were nothing short of perfection‚Äîcrisp crusts, perfectly balanced toppings, and flavors that hit all the right notes. It‚Äôs always a delight to see consistency in quality and taste.

What‚Äôs even better is that they‚Äôve opened another branch, making it easier for more pizza lovers to enjoy their delicious creations. Whether you‚Äôre a fan of traditional flavors or looking to try something new, Captain‚Äôs Oven delivers a pizza experience that‚Äôs hard to beat. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ted Gould","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfi4q0CQOsJEAVRYDXJEdKJ_Mk-Kyp_l5OYNZB3Fn501cTzfk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Crispy yet chewy sourdough crust, undeniably fresh, high quality ingredients, and an amazing array of premium pizza recipes that left me astounded. Neapolitan style should always be a go-to, but something about that impressive oven and the cooking skills at this store Sets. It. Apart.

Managed to catch the soft opening this weekend, and this is a next-level pizza place! Love the modern feel to the store, great location near the Sapperton skytrain and an apparently home-made Tiramisu capped an amazing experience! Thank you Captains Oven, you'll be seeing us again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSDjoIMCC1pD46hN8Xy-VvhMoL9grdG_8euoha&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Jason B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHPM8xPtM44eW0tBpsv7VOKz7lXS8yUYGfOoO1EucOe6ha=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible quality ingredients, great people behind the counter and care put into each pie . I would consider myself a pizza enthusiast... which is nothing to be proud of haha but this is seriously one of the best sourdough pizza's I have ever had. We have tried six pizza's so far since opening, and every order has been cooked to perfection. Recommend, any pizza but for my wife and two year old, it's the Spicy Soppressata at the current favourite. The only thing I am not happy about is they are so close, and we will be spending a lot of money there haha! Thank you for being here and see you soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmzbJdgK0WwsBmCBR8Br7co4jUmXQukaFyvoI&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-12"}]
